Whether you're tackling tough terrain or navigating the daily commute, this truck has the strength and agility to handle it all.The exterior of the Warlock is designed to turn heads, featuring a bold and distinctive style that commands attention. The Warlock interior accents and black exterior mirrors add a unique and stylish touch to the overall design.With a list price of $31,995, this 2024 Ram 1500 Classic Warlock represents an exceptional value in the full-size pickup segment. Don't miss your chance to experience the power, capability, and style of this remarkable vehicle. Visit our showroom today and let us demonstrate why the Warlock is the perfect choice for your next adventure.

description: - 1,598 miles - #43 of only 96 examples produced -The 2025 Cadillac CT5-V Blackwing ""Le Monstre"" Edition is an ultra-limited production model, with only 96 units built to commemorate Cadillac's 1950 Le Mans entry by Briggs Cunningham with two Series 61 sedans, one of which was a heavily modified aerodynamic coupe, nicknamed Le Monstre.The vehicle features a unique blue-tinted carbon fiber package, ""Magnus Metal Frost"" exterior paint, blue brake calipers, and other commemorative details like laser-etched sill plates. The vehicle retains the factory 6.2L supercharged V8 engine with 668 horsepower and 659 lb-ft of torque, paired with a manual transmission.SpecificationLe Monstre Special Edition Pack - (Front Unique Sill Plate, Santorini Seat Belts, Gloss Black Nameplates, Blue Front and Rear Calipers, Black Wheel Locks and Black Wheel Lug Nuts). Leather-Wrapped Thick Rim Steering Wheel, 3.73 Rear Axle Ratio, Inside Rear view Auto-Dimming Mirror, Electronic Cruise Control with Set and Resume Speed , Brembo 4-Wheel Anti lock High-Performance Brakes, 19"" Aluminum Alloy with Polished/dark Android Gloss Finish Wheels, 6-Speed Manual Transmission, Carbon Fiber 2 Package, (Carbon Fiber Rocker Moldings with Extensions) Carbon Fiber 1 Package, (Carbon Fiber Front Splitter), Full Semi Aniline Leather Seats, Performance Data and Video Recorder, Ultraview Dual Pane Sunroof, Premium Carpeted Floor Mats, Highway Safety Kit, All Weather Cargo Mat, Cargo Net and Cadillac Edition First Aid Kit.At Galpin Jaguar Land Rover of Van Nuys, our commitment to our customers produces one of the most valuable assets  and that's trust! We know you can't buy trust. You have to earn it! People have come to know that they can trust Galpin for the right selection, the right price, the right service and the latest innovations. That's why 92% of our customers are either repeat, reputational or referral. That's the Power of Trust! With over 75 years of automotive excellence we offer a commitment to an open, honest, and fair shopping experience. As an auto group we represent over 12 different brands from Volkswagen, Mazda, Honda, Lotus, Ford, Land Rover, Aston Martin, Lincoln, Polestar and Volvo. We have done a great amount of work to have the perfect selection of Pre-Owned vehicles and have researched hundreds of dealerships within a set radius to ensure we are competitively priced. Come on in today to check out our selection of Pre-Owned vehicles and experience exceptional service you can trust!

description:
Elevate your driving experience with this exceptional 2021 Ram 1500 Big Horn/Lone Star. Boasting a powerful HEMI 5.7L V8 engine and an impressive 8-speed automatic transmission, this truck delivers a thrilling performance that will leave you eager to take on any road.

Key features include:
Backup Camera
Keyless Entry
Power Locks
Power Windows
SiriusXM Radio Service
Dual-Zone Automatic Climate Control
Rear Window Defroster
115V Auxiliary Rear Power Outlet
400W Inverter
Power 8-Way Driver Seat
Rear Power Sliding Window
Security Alarm
Universal Garage Door Opener

Designed with your comfort and convenience in mind, this Ram 1500 is packed with premium amenities that will elevate your driving experience. From the heated steering wheel and front seats to the advanced infotainment system, every detail has been thoughtfully crafted to ensure you enjoy the journey as much as the destination.

Beyond its impressive list of features, this truck also delivers exceptional capability. The anti-spin differential rear axle and class-IV receiver hitch make it well-equipped to handle your towing and hauling needs with ease. And with a fuel-efficient rating of 15 city/22 highway MPG, you can conquer the open road without sacrificing efficiency.

Whether you're navigating the daily commute or embarking on a weekend adventure, this 2021 Ram 1500 Big Horn/Lone Star is the perfect companion. Its striking red exterior and sleek, modern design will turn heads wherever you go, while the spacious and well-appointed interior provides a comfortable and refined driving experience.

At our dealership, we pride ourselves on our commitment to customer satisfaction. We understand that purchasing a vehicle is a significant investment, and we are dedicated to ensuring you find the perfect fit for your lifestyle and needs. Our knowledgeable sales team is here to guide you through the process and answer any questions you may have.

Don't miss your chance to experience the power and versatility of this exceptional 2021 Ram 1500 Big Horn/Lone Star. Visit our showroom today and let us demonstrate why this truck should be your next automotive partner.

Step inside and you'll find a spacious and comfortable interior, complete with premium cloth seats and a range of advanced features. The 2017 Civic LX comes standard with a multi-angle rearview camera, Bluetooth connectivity, and a 5-inch display screen, making every drive a convenient and enjoyable experience.

Safety is also a top priority in the 2017 Honda Civic LX, with features such as electronic stability control, traction control, and anti-lock brakes ensuring your peace of mind on the road. Plus, with its impressive fuel economy of up to 40 mpg on the highway, you'll save both time and money at the gas pump.

Don't miss your chance to own this top-performing and stylish sedan. Visit our dealership today to test drive the 2017 Honda Civic LX and experience the ultimate driving experience.

description:
Elevate your driving experience with this exceptional 2022 Chevrolet Tahoe High Country. Boasting a powerful EcoTec3 6.2L V8 engine, this versatile SUV delivers exceptional performance and capability, with a 10-speed automatic transmission and 4-wheel drive for confident handling in any terrain.

Highlighted features include:
Adaptive Cruise Control
Panoramic Power Sunroof
Max Trailering Package
Power-Retractable Assist Steps
Air Ride Adaptive Suspension
Bose 10-Speaker Surround Audio System
SiriusXM Radio with 360L
Enhanced Driver Information Center
Hands-Free Rear Power Programmable Liftgate
Memory Settings
Remote Start
Universal Home Remote

This Tahoe High Country also offers a wealth of advanced safety and technology features, including Enhanced Automatic Emergency Braking, Adaptive Cruise Control, Dual-Pane Power Panoramic Sunroof, and a stunning 15-inch Diagonal Multi-Color Head-Up Display. The premium leather-appointed interior provides exceptional comfort and style, with heated and ventilated front seats, a heated steering wheel, and a power-folding third-row seat for maximum versatility.

Designed to impress, the Tahoe High Country's striking exterior features Iridescent Pearl Tricoat paint, chrome accents, and 22-inch Sterling Silver Premium Painted alloy wheels, creating a commanding presence on the road. The advanced trailering capabilities, including the Integrated Trailer Brake Controller and Smart Trailer Integration Indicator, make this SUV a true workhorse, ready to handle all your towing needs.

Experience the pinnacle of Chevrolet engineering and design with this 2022 Tahoe High Country. Blending power, technology, and luxury, this SUV is the ultimate expression of Chevrolet's commitment to excellence. Contact us today to schedule a test drive and discover why the Tahoe High Country should be your next vehicle.

description:
Elevate your driving experience with the exceptional 2025 Audi RS 6 Avant performance 4.0T quattro. This stunning sports wagon combines uncompromising performance, advanced technology, and refined luxury, making it the ultimate choice for the discerning driver.

Meticulously equipped, this RS 6 Avant features an impressive array of premium features, including:
- Black Dinamica Headliner
- Soft Closing doors
- Executive Package with Heated Rear Seats, Head-Up Display, Leather Package, Power Soft-Closing Doors, and Remote Park Assist Plus
- RS Sport Suspension Plus with Dynamic Ride Control
- RS Sport Exhaust System
- Red Brake Calipers
- Luggage Compartment Adjustable Rail System Kit
- Audi First Aid Kit
- Navigation System with Audi MMI Navigation plus and Touch Response
- Adaptive Cruise Assist with Lane Guidance
- Audi Side Assist with Pre Sense Rear
- Intersection Assist
- Heated and Ventilated Front Sport Seats Plus
- Wheels: 22" Matte Gray Finish 5-Y-Spoke Design

Powered by a remarkable 4.0L V8 Turbocharged engine delivering 621 horsepower, the RS 6 Avant performance delivers exhilarating acceleration and uncompromising quattro all-wheel-drive capability. The 8-speed Tiptronic transmission and dynamic suspension system ensure a thrilling yet refined driving experience, whether you're carving through winding roads or effortlessly cruising the highway.

Beyond its exceptional performance, the RS 6 Avant also boasts a stunning exterior design that commands attention. The muscular proportions, distinctive RS styling cues, and sophisticated color palette create a bold and sophisticated presence that is sure to turn heads.

Inside, the cabin is a sanctuary of luxury and technology, with premium materials, advanced infotainment, and a wealth of comfort and convenience features that elevate every journey. From the heated and ventilated front seats to the Audi Virtual Cockpit and Head-Up Display, the RS 6 Avant is designed to keep you connected, informed, and in complete control.

Experience the pinnacle of Audi performance, utility, and refinement with the 2025 RS 6 Avant performance 4.0T quattro. This exceptional sports wagon is the embodiment of Audi's relentless pursuit of excellence, and it's waiting for you to discover its unparalleled capabilities. Schedule a test drive today and prepare to be captivated by the ultimate expression of Audi's engineering prowess.

Introducing the stunning 2024 Kia K5 GT-Line, a true masterpiece of modern automotive engineering. This captivating sedan is the perfect blend of style, performance, and cutting-edge technology, making it the ideal choice for the discerning driver.

Wrapped in the stunning Glacial White Pearl exterior, this K5 GT-Line commands attention wherever it goes. Its sleek and aerodynamic design not only looks incredible but also enhances its impressive fuel efficiency, with an EPA-estimated 25 city/33 highway MPG.

Under the hood, the 1.6L I4 DGI Turbocharged DOHC 16V LEV3-ULEV70 engine delivers an exhilarating 180 horsepower, mated to an 8-speed automatic transmission and Kia's advanced All-Wheel Drive system. This powertrain provides a thrilling driving experience, with the perfect balance of power and efficiency.

Step inside the cabin, and you'll be greeted by a host of premium features that elevate the driving experience. The heated front bucket seats, wrapped in a stylish Cloth/SynTex upholstery, provide exceptional comfort and support, while the Trunk Cargo Management System and LED Trunk Light ensure your belongings are easily accessible and well-organized.

The K5 GT-Line also boasts a comprehensive suite of advanced safety and technology features, including Apple CarPlay & Android Auto, a Navigation System, and a Rear Bumper Applique. These cutting-edge systems work together to keep you connected, entertained, and protected on the road.

With its striking good looks, impressive performance, and wealth of premium features, the 2024 Kia K5 GT-Line is a truly remarkable vehicle that deserves your attention. Experience the difference for yourself and schedule a test drive today.

Safety is also a top priority, with advanced driver-assistance technologies like Reverse Automatic Braking, Blind-Spot Detection, and Rear Cross-Traffic Alert keeping you and your loved ones protected on the road. Plus, with Subaru's renowned reputation for reliability and durability, you can rest assured that this Outback Wilderness will be a trusted companion for years to come.

description:
This 2020 Volvo V60 Cross Country T5 is a beautifully balanced luxury wagon finished in white with a black interior, offering a refined yet adventurous personality that Volvo does exceptionally well. With just 32,000 miles, two owners, and no accidents reported on the Carfax, it presents in excellent condition and feels lightly used. The Cross Country styling gives it a distinctive look, blending the elegance of a wagon with the confidence and versatility of a crossover.

Powered by the turbocharged T5 engine and equipped with all wheel drive, this V60 delivers smooth, confident performance in a wide range of driving conditions. The raised ride height and rugged design elements add capability without sacrificing ride comfort or driving refinement. It feels composed on the highway, confident in poor weather, and easy to maneuver in daily use, making it a great all around vehicle for both city driving and weekend trips.

Inside, the black interior reflects Volvos signature Scandinavian design with clean lines, high quality materials, and an airy, modern feel. The cabin is loaded with thoughtful features highlighted on the spec sheet, including advanced safety technology, a panoramic roof, premium audio, digital displays, and intuitive infotainment. Seating is comfortable and supportive, and cargo space is generous for a vehicle that still feels sleek and compact.

With its low mileage, clean history, strong safety reputation, and unique wagon based versatility, this 2020 V60 Cross Country T5 is an excellent choice for someone who wants luxury, practicality, and all weather confidence in a vehicle that stands out from the typical SUV crowd.

Visit our showroom today to witness the Enclave Avenir's unparalleled blend of style, performance, and technology. With our client-centric approach, we pride ourselves in providing drivers with an entirely new way to shop for, maintain, and embrace the Audi luxury-performance tradition. Multi-year winning recipient of Audi's prestigious Magna Society Award for incredible customer service!! Come see what makes us great!If you're looking for a dependable, adventure-ready crossover that delivers comfort, capability, and confidence, this 2022 Subaru Outback Premium is waiting for you at Audi Central Houston.

Elevate your off-road adventures with this exceptional 2022 Subaru Outback Wilderness. Boasting a robust 2.4L DOHC engine paired with Subaru's renowned Lineartronic CVT and Symmetrical All-Wheel Drive system, this rugged SUV is primed to conquer any terrain with confidence and capability.

Reverse Automatic Braking (RAB) System
Power Moonroof & Navigation & RAB
Trailer Hitch & Trailer Hitch Fascia Panel
Auto-Dimming Exterior Mirror w/Approach Light
Autumn Green Metallic Door Edge Guards

Designed to take you further, the Outback Wilderness features a host of premium amenities that elevate your driving experience. Indulge in the convenience of the Subaru STARLINK 11.6" Multimedia Navigation System, which seamlessly integrates your smartphone via Android Auto and Apple CarPlay. Enjoy the added security of the Reverse Automatic Braking System, which helps you navigate tight spaces with ease.

Step inside the rugged yet refined cabin, where the StarTex-trimmed upholstery and heated front and rear seats provide unparalleled comfort, no matter the weather. The power driver's seat and power liftgate add an extra touch of convenience, while the 6-speaker audio system and available moonroof create an immersive driving environment.

Beyond its impressive features, the Outback Wilderness boasts exceptional versatility. The generous cargo space and available trailer hitch make it the perfect companion for your outdoor adventures, whether you're hauling gear or towing a trailer. And with Subaru's renowned safety technologies, including Symmetrical All-Wheel Drive and a suite of advanced driver assistance features, you can tackle the roads with confidence.

Experience the perfect blend of capability, comfort, and technology in the 2022 Subaru Outback Wilderness. Visit our showroom today and let us help you discover the perfect vehicle to elevate your adventures.

This recent arrival is a one-owner vehicle with a Clean CARFAX and recent factory service, offering peace of mind and proven reliability. With Subarus legendary all-weather capability and a refined, comfortable interior, this Outback is built for everything from daily commutes to weekend escapes beyond the city.

Because this Outback is Subaru Certified Pre-Owned, it delivers exceptional confidence from day one. Subarus CPO program includes a 7-year or 100,000-mile powertrain warranty, a thorough 152-point inspection, and 24-hour roadside assistance. These benefits help ensure long-term dependability and reduce the stress of ownership, making this Outback a smart and secure investment for years to come.

Power comes from Subarus efficient and trusted 2.5L 4-cylinder BOXER engine, paired with a smooth CVT Lineartronic transmission and Symmetrical All-Wheel Drive. With an impressive 26 city and 33 highway MPG, this Outback balances capability and efficiency beautifully. Whether you are navigating wet Seattle streets, heading into the mountains, or cruising down the highway, this Subaru delivers confident traction and a composed ride in changing conditions.

Inside, the Outback Premium offers a spacious and thoughtfully designed cabin that emphasizes comfort and convenience. Heated front seats, a power driver seat, leather-wrapped steering wheel, and dual-zone automatic climate control create a welcoming environment for both driver and passengers. The 11.6-inch Subaru STARLINK Multimedia Plus system integrates Apple CarPlay and Android Auto, keeping navigation, music, and apps easily within reach. A wireless charger, SiriusXM capability, and steering wheel-mounted controls make every drive more enjoyable and connected.

This Outback is also equipped with an excellent array of safety and driver-assist features. Blind Spot Detection with Rear Cross Traffic Alert, Active Cruise Control, Brake Assist, Electronic Stability Control, and a rearview camera work together to enhance awareness and confidence behind the wheel. Auto high-beam headlights, fog lights, and fully automatic headlights add visibility in low-light conditions, while the hands-free power rear gate and roof rack add everyday versatility for cargo and gear.

When you purchase a Subaru from Carter Subaru Ballard, you also gain access to our exclusive Loan Cars for Life program. This valuable perk helps keep you on the road when your Subaru needs qualifying service, reinforcing our commitment to long-term customer care and convenience. It is just one of the many reasons Seattle drivers continue to trust our team.

We invite you to experience this 2022 Subaru Outback Premium in person and see how well it fits your lifestyle. Visit us today or schedule your test drive by calling (206) 782-7475 or exploring www.cartersubaruballard.com

description: The 2011 Subaru Impreza WRX STI is a performance-oriented sports sedan that blends rally-inspired engineering with daily driving practicality. Under the hood, it boasts a turbocharged 2.5-liter flat-four engine delivering impressive power to all four wheels through Subaru's legendary Symmetrical All-Wheel Drive system. The aggressive body styling, wide stance, and functional hood scoop hint at its motorsport heritage, while xenon headlights enhance visibility and give the vehicle a bold, modern appearance. The suspension is tuned for responsive handling, making it equally thrilling on twisty back roads or during spirited track-day sessions.----Inside, the 2011 WRX STI is equipped with a host of comfort and convenience features. Leather seats offer a touch of refinement, while heated front seats ensure comfort during colder months. Automatic climate control maintains ideal cabin temperature with minimal effort, and Bluetooth connectivity keeps you connected hands-free on the go. For added safety, side impact airbags provide extra protection in the event of a collision. The ergonomically designed interior complements the car's performance roots, creating an engaging yet comfortable experience for both driver and passengers. This STI is a compelling choice for enthusiasts who demand both athletic prowess and daily convenience in their vehicle.

description: There could not exist a greater chasm between the first impression given by the name Polestar and the Volvo V60 variant that wears it. This unassuming Volvo hatchback is such an introvert, it might suffer from social anxiety. Indeed, merely looking at the V60 Polestar wont be enough to let most observers grasp exactly what it is. To clear things up, it is a $62,595 wagon sized toward the small end of the mid-size class, which has been given a performance makeover by Volvos in-house tuning arm, Polestar. The Polestar is exceedingly rare, with Volvo building just 750 sedans and wagons annually since its introduction for 2015. For 2018, Volvo has chucked that engine, along with its aging six-speed automatic transaxle, in favor of a 362-hp turbo- and supercharged 2.0-liter inline-four and an eight-speed automatic. description:
Looking for a reliable and versatile vehicle that can handle all your adventures? Look no further than the 2018 Subaru Outback 2.5i Touring. With its spacious interior, advanced technology, and rugged performance, this SUV is ready to take on any journey you have planned.

Under the hood, you'll find a powerful 2.5L H4 engine that delivers 175 horsepower and 174 foot-pounds of torque. Paired with a 6-speed shiftable CVT, this Outback offers a smooth and responsive driving experience. Whether you're navigating through city streets or tackling off-road terrain, this SUV has the capability to handle it all.

Step inside and you'll be greeted with a spacious and luxurious interior. The Touring trim level offers premium leather seats, heated front and rear seats, and a power moonroof, making every ride comfortable and enjoyable. The 60/40 split-folding rear seats provide ample cargo space for all your gear, making this Outback perfect for weekend getaways or daily commutes.

But the 2018 Subaru Outback is not just about comfort and performance, it also comes equipped with the latest technology. The EyeSight Driver Assist Technology helps keep you safe on the road with features like pre-collision braking, lane departure warning, and adaptive cruise control. The STARLINK multimedia system with a 7-inch touchscreen display keeps you connected with Apple CarPlay and Android Auto integration.

Don't miss out on the opportunity to own this 2018 Subaru Outback 2.5i Touring. With its exceptional features and capabilities, it's the perfect SUV for any adventure. Visit us today for a test drive and experience the Outback for yourself!

Meet the 2018 Volkswagen Golf Alltrack TSI SEL 4Motionthe wagon for people who refuse to choose between fun and function. Tech and safety are locked in with Apple CarPlay, Android Auto, Bluetooth, navigation, adaptive cruise control, blind-spot monitoring, and a rearview camera. With wagon versatility, hatchback agility, and just enough attitude to feel special, this Golf Alltrack proves practicality doesn't have to be boring it just has to be German.

description: Adventure Awaits in a Wilderness Green Metallic 2018 Subaru Outback 2.5i: Perfect for the Road Less Traveled with Unmatched Safety and Comfort Discover the 2018 Subaru Outback 2.5i, a used vehicle meticulously designed for those who love both adventure and comfort. This Wilderness Green Metallic beauty is equipped with a 2.5L 4-Cylinder engine, ensuring a powerful yet efficient drive. The Outback s all-wheel drive and Brake Actuated Limited Slip Differential make it perfect for navigating diverse terrains, from rugged trails to city streets. Safety is paramount, with features like Blind Spot Monitor, Cross-Traffic Alert, and a suite of airbags providing peace of mind. Inside, the Outback offers a premium experience with leather seats, heated both in the front and rear, and a power-adjustable driver s seat with memory settings for ultimate comfort. The sun/moonroof invites the outdoors in, while the premium sound system and Bluetooth connection keep you entertained on long journeys. The rear spoiler and aluminum wheels add a touch of sporty elegance to its robust design. Whether you re heading to the mountains or cruising through town, the Subaru Outback 2.5i is your perfect companion, combining reliability, safety, and luxury in one versatile package. Embrace every journey with confidence and style in this remarkable SUV. Be sure to call or visit Village Pointe Toyota to discover more. Your new favorite vehicle awaits - don't let someone else drive it home!

description:
At JJS Auto Sales, we ve proudly served our community for over 16 years. During that time, we ve built our reputation on offering premium-quality vehicles that are fully serviced and fully inspected before they reach our customers.Every vehicle undergoes a comprehensive inspection process, which includes checking the tires, braking system, fluid exchanges, suspension, and a full review of all key features. Additional inspections are integrated to ensure each vehicle meets our high standards for safety, reliability, and performance.When you choose JJS Auto Sales, you re not just buying a vehicle you re investing in a dependable product backed by a decade of trust and commitment to excellence.At JJ Auto Sales, we take pride in delivering vehicles that are thoroughly inspected and serviced for your peace of mind.Our inspection process begins with a two-step system:
  • Auction House Inspection Each vehicle first undergoes an initial inspection at the auction house to ensure the most critical components are in excellent condition. This includes the powertrain, engine, transmission, and transfer case (if applicable).
  • JJS Auto Sales In-House Inspection Once the vehicle arrives at our dealership, it is subject to a comprehensive in-house inspection. Our technicians carefully review and service:
    • Airbox and cabin air filter
    • Braking system
    • Exhaust system
    • Suspension components
    • Tires
    • Full synthetic oil change
    • Fluid exchanges (if they do not meet manufacturer s specifications)
    • Complete professional detailing
    This in-house process adds another layer of quality assurance and is valued at $700.
    • To further support our customers, we also recommend an independent inspection at your preferred service center. Typically, this service ranges from $80 to $100, giving you affordable, added confidence in your purchase.As a courtesy, we provide a complimentary drop-off and pickup service within a 10-mile radius to the service center of your choice.At JJS Auto Sales, our mission is to provide you with a premium product backed by transparency, integrity, and over a decade of trusted service.JJS Auto Sales, LLC179 E 19th StHolland, MI 49423616.218.3282

description:
Welcome to Stillman Volvo. We are proud to offer this GREY 2018 Volvo V60 Cross Country 4DR WGN T5 AWD to you today for only $18,999 This V60 Cross Country has the following options: OSMIUM GREY METALLIC Safety and Security
  • Lane departure prevention - Keep it between the lines. It only takes a moment of inattention for your vehicle to drift. With lane departure prevention, your vehicle takes corrective action to help you avoid unintentionally moving out of your lane. Lane departure prevention is an extra level of safety for you and those around you.
  • Forward collision mitigation - Forward thinking. You look away for just a second and suddenly the vehicle in front of you has stopped. That's when the forward collision mitigation system comes to life. When it senses an impending impact, it will activate a combination of features to help prevent or reduce the severity of an accident. Forward collision mitigation is always looking ahead.
  • Rear camera - Watching your back! The rear camera helps you see obstacles and hazards you otherwise couldn't by showing enhanced images of what is behind you. The rear camera is an extra set of eyes that's both convenient and safe.
  • Brake assist - Stop right there. Something jumps out into the middle of the road and you need to stop now! With brake assist, you will. It uses the speed of the brake pedal's travel to sense panic braking, then applies all available power to boost your stopping power. Brake assist can stop the accident before it is one.
Technology and Telematics
  • Mobile hotspot - WiFi on the fly. Connect your devices to the Internet through your vehicle's private mobile hotspot and take the internet wherever your journey takes you, without eating up your data allowance. Find the hotspot with mobile hotspot.
To be sure you don't miss out, why not give us a call at 610-399-1300 and schedule a test drive. We are located at 1290 Wilmington Pike, West Chester PA 19382. We look forward to seeing you soon.

description:
Meticulously maintained and ready to go: this 2018 Subaru Outback 2.5i Premium arrived in such excellent condition that our shop performed only light cosmetic and safety checks, preserving its well cared for character and saving you unnecessary reconditioning time. The result is a reliable, road ready wagon that blends capability and comfort for daily driving and outdoor adventure.

Engine and performance: The efficient 2.5 liter Boxer engine and continuously variable transmission deliver smooth acceleration and strong highway fuel economy. Standard all wheel drive provides confident traction in rain, snow, and varied terrain, making the Outback ideal for year round driving and weekend escapes.

Comfort and interior: Premium trim adds refined cloth or available leatherette seating, heated front seats, power driver seat, and dual zone climate control for personalized comfort. Thoughtful cabin storage and a spacious rear seat make family trips and daily errands comfortable and convenient.

Cargo and utility: Generous cargo area with split fold rear seats and wide cargo opening simplifies loading gear, groceries, and outdoor equipment. Roof rails with integrated crossbar capability support bikes, kayaks, and rooftop cargo boxes for active lifestyles.

Technology and connectivity: User friendly infotainment system, Bluetooth hands free calling, and multiple USB ports keep devices connected and occupants entertained. Clear gauges and intuitive controls enhance driver focus and usability.

Safety and confidence: Solid safety engineering, stable handling, and comprehensive passive safety features provide peace of mind on every drive. Routine maintenance and our light dealer inspection ensure dependable stopping and performance.

Exterior and durability: Iconic Outback styling combines rugged ground clearance, protective cladding, and functional design to handle both urban streets and unpaved trails with composure.

Value and condition: Minimal shop work was required because prior care kept this Outback in exceptional shape, preserving value and delivering immediate usability. This 2018 Subaru Outback 2.5i Premium is a practical, reliable choice for buyers seeking versatility, comfort, and confidence on the road.

description: 2018 Volvo V90 Cross Country T6  White Exterior with a beautiful Tan Interior The 2018 Volvo V90 Cross Country T6 sits at the top of Volvos wagon lineupoffering unmatched luxury and performance with room, flexibility, and saftey. Powered by a turbocharged and supercharged T6 engine and equipped with Volvos advanced all-wheel-drive system, the V90 Cross Country is perfect for everyday commutes and weekend getaways no matter the weather. Inside, you will enjoy the extra trunk space, beautiful interior, premium speakers, and sunroof. This V90 is the perfect luxury SUV for drivers who value style, safety, and capability. Clean CarFax, well-maintained, and ready for you to be behind the wheel. Performance and Handling  2.0L turbocharged and supercharged inline-4 (T6)  316 horsepower and 295 lb-ft of torque  8-speed Geartronic automatic transmission  060 mph in approximately 5.8 seconds  Volvo all-wheel drive for all-weather confidence  Raised ride height with off-road-inspired suspension tuning  Drive Mode Select (Comfort, Eco, Dynamic, Off-Road)  Smooth, composed handling with long-distance cruising comfort Interior Features and Comfort  Premium leather seating with Scandinavian craftsmanship  Heated front and rear seats  Power-adjustable front seats with memory settings  Heated leather-wrapped steering wheel  Panoramic power sunroof  Four-zone automatic climate control  Real wood interior inlays and ambient cabin lighting  Expansive cargo area with flat-folding rear seats Technology and Connectivity  Volvo Sensus infotainment system with large vertical touchscreen  Integrated navigation with voice control  Premium audio system (Bowers & Wilkins)  Apple CarPlay and Android Auto  Bluetooth hands-free calling and audio streaming  Keyless entry with push-button start  Full LED headlights with Volvo Thors Hammer signature Safety and Reliability  Volvo IntelliSafe driver assistance suite  Pilot Assist semi-autonomous driving support  Adaptive cruise control with steering assist  Blind Spot Information System (BLIS)  Lane Keeping Aid and Road Sign Information  Front and rear parking sensors with rearview camera  Anti-lock braking system (ABS) with brake assist  Renowned Volvo structural safety and long-term reliability Free delivery within 150 miles Limited warranty included With a mileage of 87,200 and a CLEAN Carfax, this Volvo V90 is ready to be with you for the years to come. Contact us today to schedule your test drive! SBS Motors 3350 Broadmoor Ave SE GRAND RAPIDS, MI 49512 (616) 251-1717 sales.sbsmotors@gmail.com

Discover the perfect balance of power, capability, and sophistication in the 2018 Subaru Outback 3.6R Touring. This exceptional vehicle combines the rugged versatility of an SUV with the refined driving dynamics of a luxury sedan, making it the ideal choice for those who demand more from their daily driver.

Popular Package #3 (DISC) - Includes Rear Seatback Protector, Map & Dome Lights LED Upgrade, Auto-Dimming Exterior Mirror w/Approach Light, and Thule Crossbar Set - Touring
Splash Guards

Boasting a 3.6L Boxer H6 DOHC 24V engine and Lineartronic CVT transmission, the Outback 3.6R Touring delivers exceptional power and smooth, responsive acceleration, while the standard Symmetrical All-Wheel Drive system ensures confident handling in all driving conditions. With an EPA-estimated 20 city/27 highway MPG, this Subaru offers the perfect balance of performance and efficiency.

Beyond its impressive powertrain, the Outback 3.6R Touring is packed with a wealth of premium features that elevate the driving experience. Indulge in the luxurious comfort of perforated leather-trimmed upholstery, heated front and rear seats, and a heated steering wheel. Stay connected with the STARLINK 8.0Multimedia Navigation System, complete with Apple CarPlay and Android Auto integration.

Safety is also a top priority, with a suite of advanced driver-assistance technologies, including Eyesight Driver Assist, Blind Spot Detection, and Rear Cross-Traffic Alert, ensuring you and your loved ones arrive at your destination with confidence.

Wrapped in a stunning Blue exterior, this 2018 Subaru Outback 3.6R Touring is a true standout. With its exceptional blend of capability, technology, and style, it's the perfect companion for your next adventure, whether it's a weekend getaway or your daily commute.

Experience the difference for yourself. Visit our showroom today and let us demonstrate why the Outback 3.6R Touring is the ideal choice for discerning drivers like you.

description:
Discover the perfect blend of adventure and sophistication with this stunning 2018 Volkswagen Golf Alltrack TSI S 4Motion. Boasting a dynamic 1.8L turbocharged engine, all-wheel-drive capabilities, and a sleek green exterior, this versatile wagon is ready to elevate your driving experience.

Key features include:
LED daytime running lights
Bluetooth connectivity
Autonomous emergency braking
Apple CarPlay/Android Auto integration
Rearview and backup cameras
Automatic headlights
Touch screen controls

For added convenience and protection, this Golf Alltrack comes equipped with a premium Roadside Assistance Kit, a durable Luggage Net, and the ALLTRACK Rubber Mat Kit to keep your interior pristine.

Slip into the plush V-Tex leatherette seats, which are both heated and power-adjustable for optimal comfort. The 60/40 split-folding rear bench provides ample space for your gear, while the touchscreen infotainment system keeps you connected on the go.

Engineered for adventure, the Golf Alltrack's all-wheel-drive system and 6-speed manual transmission deliver responsive handling and confident traction, no matter the terrain. With an impressive 30 highway MPG, this vehicle blends performance and efficiency seamlessly.

Whether you're tackling the city streets or exploring the great outdoors, the 2018 Volkswagen Golf Alltrack TSI S 4Motion is the perfect companion. Experience the perfect balance of style, capability, and technology. Visit our showroom today to take this remarkable vehicle for a test drive.

Why BUY from MINI of Fairfield County? When you choose this Ice Silver Metallic 2018 Subaru Outback Premium with 53,882 miles, you are not just buying a used vehicle - you are investing in quality, reliability and peace of mind. Our clientele depend on us for Transparent Pricing, Convenience and, most importantly, Customer FIRST Service! No Accidents! What this vehicle includes: STANDARD MODEL, ICE SILVER METALLIC, SLATE BLACK, CLOTH UPHOLSTERY Standard Model
    Convenience
    • Cruise control with steering wheel mounted controls. Set it and forget it. Road trips used to be stressful, until cruise control set the pace. Simply set the desired speed using the steering wheel mounted controls and it will maintain that speed without driver intervention. This can help minimize driver fatigue and improve overall fuel economy. Resting your right foot is right at your fingertips thanks to cruise control with steering wheel mounted controls.
    Safety and Security
    • Rear camera - Watching your back! The rear camera helps you see obstacles and hazards you otherwise couldn't by showing enhanced images of what is behind you. The rear camera is an extra set of eyes that's both convenient and safe.
    • Brake assist - Stop right there. Something jumps out into the middle of the road and you need to stop now! With brake assist, you will. It uses the speed of the brake pedal's travel to sense panic braking, then applies all available power to boost your stopping power. Brake assist can stop the accident before it is one.
    Technology and Telematics
    • Smart device mirroring - Smartphone, meet smart car. You can control your device through your vehicle's infotainment system. Smart device mirroring brings together safety and convenience by making it easier to find what you're looking for while keeping your eyes on the road.
    • Selective Internet access - a more focused delivery. Selective internet access allows you to tailor the features for your feed, such as sports scores, local news, or current weather. When it comes to getting what you want, selective internet access is a net gain.
    Come on in to MINI of Fairfield County today at 154 Post Rd. Darien CT 06820 or call 203-348-4700 to schedule a test drive!

description:
Discover the ultimate adventure-ready companion in the 2018 Subaru Outback 2.5i Touring. This versatile and well-equipped SUV is the perfect blend of rugged capability and refined comfort, making it the ideal choice for those who seek to explore the great outdoors without sacrificing everyday practicality.

Navigation System
12 Speakers
harman/kardon Surround Sound Speaker System
Subaru STARLINK 8.0" Multimedia Nav System
Automatic Temperature Control
Power Driver Seat
Power Moonroof
Smartphone Integration
Power Liftgate
Exterior Parking Camera Rear
Auto High-Beam Headlights
Heated Steering Wheel
Perforated Leather-Trimmed Upholstery
Heated Reclining Front Bucket Seats

Powered by a robust 2.5L 4-cylinder DOHC engine and Subaru's legendary Symmetrical All-Wheel Drive system, the Outback 2.5i Touring delivers an exceptional balance of performance and efficiency. With an EPA-estimated 25 city/32 highway mpg, this SUV ensures you can venture further without frequent stops.

Elevate your driving experience with the advanced technology features that come standard. The Subaru STARLINK infotainment system, complete with an 8-inch touchscreen, provides seamless smartphone integration, navigation, and a premium harman/kardon sound system for your listening pleasure. Comfort is also a priority, with dual-zone automatic climate control, heated front and rear seats, and a power driver's seat with memory function.

Safety is paramount in the Outback 2.5i Touring, which comes equipped with a suite of advanced driver assistance technologies. Enjoy the added peace of mind of features like Eyesight Driver Assist Technology, Blind Spot Detection, and Rear Cross-Traffic Alert, all working together to help keep you and your loved ones secure on the road.

Whether you're tackling the daily commute or embarking on a weekend getaway, the 2018 Subaru Outback 2.5i Touring is the perfect companion. Its spacious interior, versatile cargo area, and impressive off-road capabilities make it a true all-around performer. Experience the perfect blend of capability, comfort, and technology by scheduling a test drive today.

description: Welcome to Stillman Volvo. We are proud to offer this WHITE 2018 Volvo V90 Cross Country 5DR T5 WGN AWD to you today for only $21,999 This V90 Cross Country has the following options: Safety and Security Forward collision mitigation - Forward thinking. You look away for just a second and suddenly the vehicle in front of you has stopped. That's when the forward collision mitigation system comes to life. When it senses an impending impact, it will activate a combination of features to help prevent or reduce the severity of an accident. Forward collision mitigation is always looking ahead. Pedestrian impact prevention - An extra step toward safety. Pedestrians don't always stop, look, and listen, but with Pedestrian Impact Prevention, your vehicle is equipped to better see them and avoid them. This system constantly monitors the road ahead to identify and track pedestrians. It projects that image to an interior display screen, AND should an impact become likely, Pedestrian impact prevention takes steps to avoid a collision. Hands-on cruise control. Set it and forget it. Road trips used to be stressful. Cruise control only managed speed, but not distance or safety. Now, with hands-on cruise control, simply set your desired speed and let sensor technology maintain a safe distance between you and surrounding vehicles. It slows you down speeds you up and even keeps you in your own lane. Meet your ultimate co-pilot with hands-on cruise control. Technology and Telematics Smart device mirroring - Smartphone, meet smart car. You can control your device through your vehicle's infotainment system. Smart device mirroring brings together safety and convenience by making it easier to find what you're looking for while keeping your eyes on the road. Mobile hotspot - WiFi on the fly. Connect your devices to the Internet through your vehicle's private mobile hotspot and take the internet wherever your journey takes you, without eating up your data allowance. Find the hotspot with mobile hotspot. To be sure you don't miss out, why not give us a call at 610-399-1300 and schedule a test drive. We are located at 1290 Wilmington Pike, West Chester PA 19382. We look forward to seeing you soon.Plus, tax, dealer DOC fee of $477.00, title registration.

description:
This 2018 Subaru Outback 2.5i Limited in White is a remarkable SUV that combines exceptional capability, advanced technology, and uncompromising comfort. With its spacious interior, refined driving dynamics, and comprehensive safety features, this Outback is the perfect companion for your adventures, whether you're navigating the city streets or exploring the great outdoors.

2018 Subaru Outback 2.5i Limited in White
Protection Package #1 with Rear Seatback Protector, Splash Guards, Wheel Arch Moldings, and All-Weather Floor Liners
Harman/Kardon Surround Sound Speaker System
Subaru STARLINK 8.0" Multimedia Plus System with Apple CarPlay and Android Auto
Power Moonroof
Exterior Parking Camera Rear
Heated Reclining Front Bucket Seats
18" Aluminum Alloy Wheels

Powered by a robust 2.5L 4-cylinder DOHC 16V engine and Lineartronic CVT, this Outback delivers an impressive blend of performance and efficiency, with an EPA-estimated 25 city/32 highway MPG. The Symmetrical All-Wheel Drive system ensures confident handling and traction in a variety of road conditions, making it a versatile choice for your daily commute or weekend adventures.

Inside, the Outback 2.5i Limited pampers you with a wealth of premium features. The leather-trimmed upholstery, heated front seats, and power-adjustable driver's seat provide unparalleled comfort, while the Harman/Kardon surround sound system and 8-inch STARLINK multimedia display keep you entertained and connected on the go.

Safety is a top priority in the Outback, and this model is equipped with a comprehensive suite of advanced safety technologies, including Eyesight Driver Assist, Blind Spot Detection, and Rear Cross-Traffic Alert. You can drive with confidence, knowing that you and your passengers are well-protected.

Whether you're seeking a capable and versatile SUV for your daily commute or a rugged companion for your outdoor pursuits, this 2018 Subaru Outback 2.5i Limited is an exceptional choice. We invite you to experience the exceptional quality, performance, and features that make this Outback a standout in its class. Visit our showroom today and let us demonstrate how this remarkable vehicle can enhance your driving experience.

Discover the perfect blend of capability, comfort, and style with this 2018 Subaru Outback 2.5i Touring. This exceptional SUV-like crossover is packed with premium features that elevate your driving experience to new heights.

Highlights of this Outback include:
Crystal White Pearl Body Side Molding
Auto-Dimming Exterior Mirror w/Approach Light
Splash Guards
Crystal White Pearl Door Edge Guards
All-Weather Floor Liners
Rear Seatback Protector
Cargo Net

Beyond these thoughtful additions, this Outback offers a wealth of desirable amenities. Enjoy the convenience of the Subaru STARLINK 8.0" Multimedia Navigation System, the premium sound of the harman/kardon Surround Sound Speaker System, and the comfort of heated front and rear seats. The power moonroof and power liftgate add to the Outback's versatility, while features like Smartphone Integration, Auto High-Beam Headlights, and Blind-Spot Detection with Lane Change Assist enhance your safety and connectivity.

Powered by Subaru's renowned 2.5L 4-cylinder DOHC engine paired with a smooth Lineartronic CVT and Symmetrical All-Wheel Drive, this Outback delivers an impressive balance of performance and efficiency, with an EPA-estimated 25 MPG in the city and 32 MPG on the highway.

Whether you're tackling your daily commute or embarking on an adventure, this 2018 Subaru Outback 2.5i Touring is ready to elevate your driving experience. With its exceptional capabilities, premium features, and timeless style, this Outback is the perfect companion for the discerning buyer. Visit our showroom today to experience it for yourself and discover why the Outback is the ultimate crossover.

Introducing the 2017 Subaru Outback 2.5i Premium, the perfect vehicle for all your adventures. With its spacious interior, rugged capabilities, and advanced technology, this Subaru Outback is ready to take you on any journey.

Step inside and experience the premium comfort of the Outback's refined interior. With ample legroom and cargo space, you and your passengers will have plenty of room to stretch out and relax. Don't miss your chance to own this 2017 Subaru Outback 2.5i Premium. Visit our dealership today and experience the ultimate blend of versatility, comfort, and performance. With its sleek design and impressive features, this Outback is sure to turn heads wherever you go. So why wait? Take the wheel and start your next adventure in the 2017 Subaru Outback.

The integrated turn signal mirrors and automatic headlights enhance visibility, while the rearview camera aids in effortless parking. Enjoy seamless connectivity with Bluetooth, smart device integration, and a premium sound system, making every drive both entertaining and convenient. Whether you re navigating city streets or exploring off the beaten path, the Subaru Outback 2.5i is equipped to support your lifestyle with its blend of rugged capability and refined comfort. description:
Two owner and a clean Carfax: this 2017 Volkswagen Golf Alltrack TSI SEL 4Motion arrived in such exceptional condition that our technicians completed only light inspection and detail work, preserving its well cared for character and getting it road ready quickly. The documented history and careful ownership show in the tidy interior, solid mechanical condition, and crisp exterior finish.

Versatile performance and capability: Powered by a turbocharged TSI engine and equipped with Volkswagen 4Motion all wheel drive, the Golf Alltrack delivers confident traction, composed handling, and spirited acceleration for highway cruising and weekend adventures. Smooth shifting and refined suspension tuning combine efficiency and engagement for daily driving and touring.

Premium SEL trim and comfort: SEL specification adds upscale features including leather seating surfaces, heated front seats, power adjustable driver seat, dual zone climate control, and upgraded interior trim for a refined driving environment. Spacious cargo area and rear seats that fold flat provide practical versatility for gear, luggage, and lifestyle needs.

Technology and connectivity: The intuitive infotainment touchscreen supports Apple CarPlay and Android Auto for seamless smartphone integration. Bluetooth hands free calling, navigation ready capability, and multiple USB ports keep occupants connected and entertained on every trip. Clear instrument cluster and steering wheel controls enhance driver focus and convenience.

Safety and driver confidence: Comprehensive safety engineering, stability control, traction management, and multiple airbags contribute to occupant protection and confident handling in varied road conditions. Routine maintenance and our light dealer inspection support reliable stopping and performance.

Exterior utility and styling: Rugged wagon styling, roof rails, and protective body cladding combine function and form, making the Golf Alltrack a stylish choice for outdoor activities and urban driving alike. Alloy wheels and fog lights add to both utility and curb appeal.

Value and condition: Two owner history, a clean Carfax, and minimal dealer reconditioning make this 2017 Volkswagen Golf Alltrack TSI SEL 4Motion an excellent option for buyers seeking a well maintained, feature rich compact wagon with versatile capability. Financing and extended warranty options are available.

Contact us today to schedule a test drive!

description:
Why BUY from Subaru Olathe? When you choose this Crystal White Pearl 2017 Subaru Outback Premium with 57,098 miles, you are not just buying a used vehicle - you are investing in quality, reliability and peace of mind. Our clientele depend on us for Transparent Pricing, Convenience and, most importantly, Customer FIRST Service! No Doc Fees. No Add-Ons. No Suprises! One Owner! What this vehicle includes: EyeSight and Blind Spot and Rear Cross Traffic ($1,995 value)
  • Blind Spot Detection (BSD)
  • Rear Cross Traffic Alert (RCTA)
  • EyeSight System with Lane Keep Assist
  • High Beam Assist
  • Power Rear Gate with Automatic Close and Height Memory
EyeSight System with Lane Keep Assist
  • Adaptive Cruise Control
  • Lane Departure Warning
  • Pre-Collision System
Convenience
  • Distance pacing cruise control - Set it and forget it. Road trips used to be stressful. Cruise control only managed speed, but not distance or safety. Now, with Distance pacing cruise control, simply set your desired speed and let sensor technology maintain a safe distance between you and the vehicle ahead. Distance pacing cruise control, your ultimate co-pilot.
Safety and Security
  • Forward collision mitigation - Forward thinking. You look away for just a second and suddenly the vehicle in front of you has stopped. That's when the forward collision mitigation system comes to life. When it senses an impending impact, it will activate a combination of features to help prevent or reduce the severity of an accident. Forward collision mitigation is always looking ahead.
  • Rear camera - Watching your back! The rear camera helps you see obstacles and hazards you otherwise couldn't by showing enhanced images of what is behind you. The rear camera is an extra set of eyes that's both convenient and safe.
  • Brake assist - Stop right there. Something jumps out into the middle of the road and you need to stop now! With brake assist, you will. It uses the speed of the brake pedal's travel to sense panic braking, then applies all available power to boost your stopping power. Brake assist can stop the accident before it is one.
Technology and Telematics
  • Selective Internet access - a more focused delivery. Selective internet access allows you to tailor the features for your feed, such as sports scores, local news, or current weather. When it comes to getting what you want, selective internet access is a net gain.
EYESIGHT & BLIND SPOT & REAR CROSS TRAFFIC & PRG, CRYSTAL WHITE PEARL, SLATE BLACK, CLOTH UPHOLSTERY, EXTERIOR AUTO DIMMING MIRROR FOR BSD, SPLASH GUARDS, REAR BUMPER COVER, ALL WEATHER FLOOR MATS Come on in to Subaru Olathe today at 16540 W 119th St. Olathe KS 66061 or call 816-200-2173 to schedule a test drive!

Introducing the 2024 Subaru Outback Touring - a versatile and capable SUV that's ready to take you on your next adventure. With its sleek exterior, advanced technology, and premium features, this Outback is the perfect companion for those who demand more from their vehicle.

Collision Warning System

Under the hood, this Outback Touring is powered by a robust 2.5L 4-Cylinder DOHC 16V engine, mated to a smooth and efficient CVT Lineartronic transmission. With Subaru's legendary Symmetrical All-Wheel Drive system, you'll have the confidence to tackle any terrain, whether it's a winding mountain road or a snowy backroad. And with an impressive EPA-estimated 26 MPG in the city and 32 MPG on the highway, you'll enjoy exceptional fuel efficiency without sacrificing performance.

The interior of the Outback Touring is equally impressive, with a host of premium features that elevate the driving experience. Sink into the comfortable and supportive Nappa leather-trimmed seats, which are both heated and ventilated for year-round comfort. The 11.6-inch STARLINK Multimedia Navigation System keeps you connected and entertained, while the 12-speaker harman/kardon audio system delivers an immersive listening experience.

Safety is also a top priority in the Outback Touring, with advanced driver-assist technologies like Collision Warning System, Blind-Spot Monitors, and Lane Keeping Assist. The STARLINK Safety Plus system even provides emergency communication services, giving you added peace of mind on the road.

Whether you're tackling the daily commute or planning a weekend getaway, the 2024 Subaru Outback Touring is the perfect companion. With its impressive capabilities, premium features, and exceptional value, this Outback is sure to exceed your expectations. Visit our showroom today to experience it for yourself and discover why the Outback Touring is the ultimate adventure-ready SUV.

Whether you're embarking on a family road trip, navigating the daily commute, or exploring the great outdoors, this 2024 Subaru Outback Premium is the perfect companion. Experience the perfect blend of style, technology, and practicality with the 2024 Kia Soul LX. This exceptional compact SUV is the ideal companion for your urban adventures, offering a spacious interior, impressive fuel efficiency, and a host of advanced features that will elevate your driving experience.

Unlock a world of convenience and safety with the impressive list of features included in this Kia Soul LX:

LX Technology Package: Blind-Spot Collision-Avoidance Assist, Lane Change Assist, Rear Cross-Traffic Collision Avoidance Assist, 6.5J x 16" Alloy Wheels
Apple CarPlay & Android Auto
Blind-Spot Collision-Avoidance Assist
Lane Change Assist
Rear Cross-Traffic Collision Avoidance Assist
6.5J x 16" Alloy Wheels

Kia's commitment to quality and reliability is evident in this certified pre-owned Soul LX. With a 165-point inspection, roadside assistance, and comprehensive warranty coverage, you can drive with confidence, knowing your investment is protected.

The 2024 Kia Soul LX boasts a 2.0L I4 DOHC engine that delivers an exceptional blend of power and efficiency, with an EPA-estimated 29 MPG in the city and 35 MPG on the highway. This means you'll spend less time at the pump and more time exploring the open road.

Stepping inside the Soul LX, you'll be greeted by a spacious and well-appointed interior, featuring comfortable cloth seating, a user-friendly infotainment system, and a host of convenient amenities. Whether you're commuting to work or embarking on a weekend adventure, the Soul LX is designed to make every journey a pleasure.

Versatility is at the heart of the Kia Soul LX, with a generous cargo area and split-folding rear seats that allow you to accommodate your ever-changing lifestyle needs. From hauling bulky items to transporting your active lifestyle gear, this compact SUV has you covered.

As a Kia Certified Pre-Owned vehicle, this 2024 Soul LX comes with the peace of mind of a 12-month/12,000-mile "Platinum Coverage" limited warranty, as well as a 120-month/100,000-mile powertrain warranty. Additionally, you'll enjoy the benefits of roadside assistance and rental car reimbursement, ensuring a seamless ownership experience.

Don't miss your chance to make the 2024 Kia Soul LX your own. Visit our showroom today and let us demonstrate how this exceptional compact SUV can enhance your driving life.

Powered by a robust 2.5L 4-cylinder DOHC 16V engine and Subaru's legendary Symmetrical All-Wheel Drive system, the Outback Premium delivers an impressive 26 city/32 highway MPG, ensuring efficient performance for your everyday journeys and weekend adventures.

Elevate your driving experience with the Subaru STARLINK 11.6" Multimedia Navigation System, featuring voice-activated controls, wireless Apple CarPlay and Android Auto integration, and a high-resolution display that puts your world at your fingertips. The Hands-Free Power Rear Gate and Keyless Access with Push Button Start add a touch of convenience, while the Power Moonroof and All-Weather Floor Liners enhance your comfort and versatility.

This Subaru Certified Pre-Owned Outback Premium has been meticulously inspected and comes with a comprehensive warranty and additional benefits, giving you the peace of mind you deserve. Enjoy the confidence of a 152-Point Inspection, Roadside Assistance, a Transferable Warranty, and a Powertrain Limited Warranty that extends up to 84 months or 100,000 miles from the original in-service date.

Discover the perfect blend of capability, technology, and refinement in the 2024 Subaru Outback Premium. Experience the difference that Subaru's commitment to quality and customer satisfaction can make. Visit Subaru of Las Vegas today and let our dedicated Purchase Advisor guide you through the seamless car-buying process.

Discover smart design, advanced safety, and outstanding efficiency in this SNOW WHITE PEARL 2023 KIA SOUL LX FWD, now available at KIA OF ORANGE PARK. Drive with confidence knowing your engine and transmission are covered for as long as you own the vehicle.

Helps detect potential front-end collisions and can automatically apply braking to help reduce or avoid impacts.

Assists with steering to help keep your Kia Soul centered in its lane, reducing driver fatigue on longer drives.

LANE KEEPING ASSIST
Provides gentle steering corrections if you begin to drift out of your lane without signaling.

DRIVER ATTENTION WARNING
Monitors driving patterns and alerts you if signs of fatigue or inattention are detected.

HIGH BEAM ASSIST
Automatically adjusts between high and low beams to improve nighttime visibility without blinding other drivers.

8" TOUCHSCREEN w/ANDROID AUTO & APPLE CARPLAY

USB MULTIMEDIA PORT
Keep your devices charged and connected for music streaming and hands-free convenience.

REMOTE KEYLESS ENTRY
Unlock and lock your vehicle effortlessly for added convenience and security.

REAR OCCUPANT ALERT
Provides reminders to check the rear seats, adding an extra layer of safety for families.

AUTO-ON/OFF HEADLIGHTS
Automatically activate based on lighting conditions, enhancing visibility and convenience.

16" STEEL WHEELS WITH WHEEL COVERS
Durable and efficient wheels designed for a smooth ride and low maintenance ownership.

CALL US FOR VEHICLE AVAILABILITY AT 904-771-6078
ASK ABOUT OUR LIFETIME POWERTRAIN WARRANTY

Dont miss your chance to own this reliable and fuel-efficient 2023 KIA SOUL LX. Visit KIA OF ORANGE PARK today and see why so many drivers choose us for quality vehicles and exceptional service!

Vehicle Details
2023 Subaru Outback Premium 32,372 miles Fletcher, NC. This AWD wagon pairs confident all-weather capability with a fuel-efficient 2.5L 4-cylinder engine, making it an ideal choice for daily commutes and weekend escapes. Well-equipped and thoughtfully maintained, the Subaru Outback Premium includes XM Radio, Back-Up Camera, Automatic Climate Control, and a CARFAX Clean Report with CARFAX 1-Owner history for added peace of mind. Inside, the comfortable cabin offers versatile cargo space and user-friendly controls, while Subaru's Symmetrical AWD delivers stability and traction on wet or slippery roads. With modern infotainment and convenience features, this Subaru Outback balances practicality and comfort without compromising reliability. The efficient 2.5L engine provides responsive performance and good fuel economy for highway cruising or mountain drives around Fletcher and Western North Carolina. Priced to sell, this 2023 Subaru Outback Premium features the best price for comparable vehicles in the area an excellent value backed by clear ownership history. Located in Fletcher, NC, the vehicle is ready for a test drive today. Contact us to schedule a viewing, request the CARFAX report, or get pre-approved financing. Act now to secure this AWD Subaru Outback with low miles and top features at an unbeatable price.

Equipment
This model offers Apple CarPlay for seamless connectivity. Lane Keep Assist in this unit helps maintain safe driving by gently steering to stay within the lane. Bluetooth technology is built into this 2023 Subaru Outback , keeping your hands on the steering wheel and your focus on the road. This Subaru Outback comes equipped with Android Auto for seamless smartphone integration on the road. This model keeps you comfortable with Auto Climate. This unit has auto-adjust speed for safe following. It has a clean CARFAX vehicle history report. This vehicle is a certified CARFAX 1-owner. See what's behind you with the back up camera on it. with XM/Sirus Satellite Radio you are no longer restricted by poor quality local radio stations while driving this model. Anywhere on the planet, you will have hundreds of digital stations to choose from. Set the temperature exactly where you are most comfortable in this model. The fan speed and temperature will automatically adjust to maintain your preferred zone climate.

Packages
Standard Model. Auto-Dimming Mirror with Compass and HomeLink. **Equipment listed is based on original vehicle build and subject to change. Please confirm the accuracy of the included equipment by calling the dealer prior to purchase.**

Additional Information
Hunter Auto Group has been family-owned and operated since 1940 and offers a comprehensive vehicle inspection on every pre-owned vehicle we sell. Have peace of mind with every vehicle being quality inspected and repaired by top-notch mechanics. We also offer market-based pricing on every car we sell so You never pay too much. Come on in today and experience the Hunter way of doing business. We look forward to serving you.

Elevate your driving experience with this stunning 2023 Subaru Outback Limited. This versatile and capable SUV is the perfect companion for your adventures, offering a seamless blend of style, performance, and cutting-edge technology.

Power Moonroof & HSW & Navigation System

DriverFocus (Driver Monitoring System)

Boasting a 2.5L 4-Cylinder DOHC 16V engine paired with Subaru's renowned Lineartronic CVT and Symmetrical All-Wheel Drive, this Outback delivers an exceptional driving experience. With an impressive 26 city/32 highway MPG, you can explore the open road with confidence and efficiency.

Step inside and be captivated by the luxurious Perforated Leather-Trimmed Upholstery, Heated Front Bucket Seats, and Heated Rear Seats, creating a truly comfortable and indulgent cabin. The Subaru STARLINK 11.6" Multimedia Navigation System, complete with a 576-watt Harman Kardon surround sound system, ensures you stay connected and entertained on every journey.

For added convenience and peace of mind, this Outback Limited is equipped with a Power Liftgate, Auto-Dimming Exterior Mirrors with Approach Light, and a Wireless Charger, seamlessly integrating technology into your daily driving.

As a Subaru Certified Pre-Owned vehicle, this Outback has undergone a rigorous 152-point inspection and comes with a Powertrain Limited Warranty of 84 Months/100,000 Miles, Roadside Assistance, and a $0 Deductible. You can drive with confidence, knowing this Outback is backed by Subaru's renowned quality and reliability.

Fuel Tank, Wheels: 7J x 17\' 10-Spoke Alloy, Radio w/Seek-Scan, Clock, Speed Compensated Volume Control, Steering Wheel Controls and Radio Data System, Bluetooth Wireless Phone Connectivity, Heated Front Bucket Seats -inc: armrests, seatback pockets, 6-way adjustable driver's seat w/power lumbar support and 4-way adjustable fold-flat front passenger seat, 60-40 Folding Split-Bench Front Facing Manual Reclining Fold Forward Seatback Rear Seat w/Manual Fore/Aft, Selective Service Internet Access, Automatic Air Conditioning w/Steering Wheel Controls, Full Floor Console w/Covered Storage, Mini Overhead Console w/Storage and 2 12V DC Power Outlets Convenience
  • Distance pacing cruise control - Set it and forget it. Road trips used to be stressful. Cruise control only managed speed, but not distance or safety. Now, with Distance pacing cruise control, simply set your desired speed and let sensor technology maintain a safe distance between you and the vehicle ahead. Distance pacing cruise control, your ultimate co-pilot.
Safety and Security
  • Forward collision mitigation - Forward thinking. You look away for just a second and suddenly the vehicle in front of you has stopped. That's when the forward collision mitigation system comes to life. When it senses an impending impact, it will activate a combination of features to help prevent or reduce the severity of an accident. Forward collision mitigation is always looking ahead.
  • Rear camera - Watching your back! The rear camera helps you see obstacles and hazards you otherwise couldn't by showing enhanced images of what is behind you. The rear camera is an extra set of eyes that's both convenient and safe.
  • Brake assist - Stop right there. Something jumps out into the middle of the road and you need to stop now! With brake assist, you will. It uses the speed of the brake pedal's travel to sense panic braking, then applies all available power to boost your stopping power. Brake assist can stop the accident before it is one.
Technology and Telematics
  • Selective Internet access - a more focused delivery. Selective internet access allows you to tailor the features for your feed, such as sports scores, local news, or current weather. When it comes to getting what you want, selective internet access is a net gain.

Here at Via Auto Sales, we can help you get your car with NO Co-Signer!! You'll be able to own your first vehicle, get a great interest rate and start building your credit all without a Co-Signer!! Extended Warranties Available!! CALL OR EMAIL US TODAY! Meet this 2014 Subaru Outback 3.6R Limited  a nicely equipped, one-owner wagon finished in striking Blue with a warm Tan leather interior. Under the hood is Subarus smooth 3.6L H6 engine producing 256 hp and 247 lb-ft of torque, paired with Subarus proven Symmetrical All-Wheel Drive and a 5-speed automatic transmission for composed, confident driving in all kinds of weather. This Outback has excellent overall condition, a clean CARFAX, and under 95,000 miles (averaging less than 8,000 miles per year). EPA fuel economy is 17 MPG city / 25 MPG highway. Factory-equipped highlights - Performance and drivetrain: 3.6L H6 256 hp / 247 lb-ft, 5-speed automatic transmission with manual mode, Symmetrical All-Wheel Drive for improved traction and stability. - Exterior and utility: Blue exterior paint, roof rails with integrated crossbars for bikes or cargo carriers, fog lights, projector-style headlights, and 18-inch alloy wheels with all-season tires. 60/40 split-folding rear seat expands cargo flexibility for larger loads. - Comfort and convenience: Tan leather-trimmed seating, heated front seats, power-adjustable drivers seat (including memory settings) and power passenger seat, tilt/telescoping steering column, dual-zone automatic climate control, and ample interior storage with a center console armrest. - Glass and roof: Powered moonroof/sunroof to let in light and fresh airgreat for long drives or scenic routes. - Technology and audio: Factory stereo with CD player, AM/FM, USB/AUX inputs and Bluetooth hands-free connectivity for phone calls and audio streaming, steering-wheel-mounted audio and phone controls for safer operation on the go. Satellite radio capability was supported. - Safety: Multiple airbags including front, side and curtain airbags, ABS brakes, traction and stability control, brake assist, and tire pressure monitoring system. A rearview camera was included on many Outback Limited models for easier, safer reversing. Lower anchors and tethers for child seats (LATCH) are in back seats. - Convenience features: Keyless access with push-button start for quick entry and easy starts, remote keyless entry, power windows and door locks, and cruise control for relaxed highway driving. Why this Outback stands out This 3.6R Limited blends Subarus rally-proven AWD capability with a powerful H6 engine and a well-appointed interior. With one careful owner, a clean CARFAX, sensible mileage under 95k, and excellent overall condition, its a great choice if you want a practical, capable wagon thats comfortable for daily driving and confident on weekend adventures. Don't miss out on the opportunity to own a piece of automotive excellence - the 2014 Subaru Outback 2.5i Limited.

description: Discover the Joy of Driving with the 2014 Subaru Impreza 2.0i: Where Performance Meets Versatility in a Sleek Ice Silver Metallic Hatchback The 2014 Subaru Impreza 2.0i is the perfect companion for those who crave a blend of performance and practicality. With its robust 2.0L 4-Cylinder engine and CVT Lineartronic transmission, this hatchback offers a smooth and responsive drive, effortlessly handling both city streets and winding country roads. Its all-wheel-drive capability ensures confidence and stability, no matter the weather or terrain. Safety is paramount in the Impreza, featuring an array of protective measures like automatic headlights, brake assist, and a comprehensive airbag system, including knee and side airbags. The traction and stability control systems further enhance your peace of mind, making every journey secure. Inside, the Impreza caters to the tech-savvy driver with Bluetooth connectivity and steering wheel audio controls, allowing you to stay connected and entertained on the go. The versatile interior boasts comfortable cloth bucket seats and a pass-through rear seat, offering ample space for both passengers and cargo. Finished in an elegant Ice Silver Metallic, this 4D hatchback is not just a vehicle it s a lifestyle choice for those who appreciate reliability, safety, and a touch of sophistication in their daily drive. Be sure to call or visit Camelback VW Subaru to discover more. Your new favorite vehicle awaits - don't let someone else drive it home!

description:
Discover the perfect balance of capability, comfort, and style in this 2014 Subaru Outback 2.5i Limited. With its impressive all-wheel-drive performance, advanced safety features, and premium amenities, this Outback is poised to elevate your driving experience.

Highlighted features include:
Bluetooth
Leather-trimmed upholstery
Heated front seats
Power windows and locks
Special Appearance Package & EyeSight

The Outback's 2.5L 4-cylinder DOHC engine, paired with Subaru's renowned Lineartronic CVT, delivers a smooth and efficient driving dynamic, offering 24 city/30 highway MPG. Elevate your commute or weekend adventures with the available navigation system, harman/kardon premium sound system, and adaptive cruise control.

Safety is paramount in the Outback, with cutting-edge technologies like the EyeSight driver assist system, lane departure warning, and pre-collision braking. Enjoy the peace of mind that comes with Subaru's commitment to safety and reliability.

The Outback's versatile interior features a spacious cargo area, split-folding rear seats, and a host of premium touches, including a power driver's seat, dual-zone climate control, and a rearview camera. With the added convenience of keyless access and push-button start, you'll be ready to tackle any journey with ease.

Distinctive exterior details, such as the gray exterior door handles, foldable mirrors, and Outback-style grille, lend an elegant and refined appearance. The 17-inch alloy wheels with a machine finish complement the Outback's sleek design.

Experience the perfect blend of capability, comfort, and style in this 2014 Subaru Outback 2.5i Limited. Schedule a test drive today and discover why this Outback is the ideal companion for your next adventure.

description:
Discover the perfect blend of efficiency and sophistication in this 2014 Toyota Prius v Five. With its impressive fuel economy, advanced technology features, and premium styling, this exceptional hybrid vehicle is the ideal choice for the eco-conscious driver who demands more.

Boasting a robust list of sought-after amenities, this Prius v Five is sure to impress. Key highlights include:

Navigation System
6 Speakers
AM/FM radio: SiriusXM
CD player
Air Conditioning
Automatic temperature control
Power windows
Remote keyless entry
Steering wheel mounted audio controls
3-Door Smart Key System w/Push Button Start
ABS brakes
Dual front impact airbags
Dual front side impact airbags
Brake assist
Electronic Stability Control
Exterior Parking Camera Rear

Slip behind the wheel of this well-equipped Prius v and experience the perfect harmony of performance and environmental responsibility. The 1.8L 4-Cylinder DOHC 16V VVT-i Aluminum engine, paired with a CVT transmission, delivers an exceptional 44 city/40 highway MPG, allowing you to go farther on every tank of gas.

The striking red exterior complements the spacious and well-appointed interior, featuring SofTex seat trim, heated front seats, and a wealth of advanced technology. The intuitive navigation system, coupled with the premium sound system, will keep you connected and entertained on every journey.

Safety is also a top priority, with features like ABS brakes, dual front and side impact airbags, and Electronic Stability Control providing added peace of mind. The Exterior Parking Camera Rear further enhances your driving confidence, making maneuvering and parking a breeze.

This 2014 Toyota Prius v Five is a testament to the brand's commitment to innovation and sustainability. With its unparalleled efficiency, comprehensive list of features, and impeccable design, it's the perfect choice for the environmentally conscious driver who refuses to compromise on style or technology.

We invite you to experience the exceptional qualities of this Prius v for yourself. Schedule a test drive today and discover the perfect blend of eco-friendly performance and premium amenities that will exceed your expectations.

Convenience
  • Cruise control with steering wheel mounted controls. Set it and forget it. Road trips used to be stressful, until cruise control set the pace. Simply set the desired speed using the steering wheel mounted controls and it will maintain that speed without driver intervention. This can help minimize driver fatigue and improve overall fuel economy. Resting your right foot is right at your fingertips thanks to cruise control with steering wheel mounted controls.
Safety and Security
  • Rear camera - Watching your back! The rear camera helps you see obstacles and hazards you otherwise couldn't by showing enhanced images of what is behind you. The rear camera is an extra set of eyes that's both convenient and safe.
  • Brake assist - Stop right there. Something jumps out into the middle of the road and you need to stop now! With brake assist, you will. It uses the speed of the brake pedal's travel to sense panic braking, then applies all available power to boost your stopping power. Brake assist can stop the accident before it is one.
About Dublin Honda Not only are we Honda enthusiasts at Dublin Honda, we're dedicated members of the local community. Ken Harvey opened Dublin Honda in 1977 and has helped literally thousands upon thousands of Happy Honda Owners find and maintain their Hondas. To this day, Dublin Honda remains a family-owned and family-operated dealership, committed to the local community we serve and in which we live.
