description: 2014 Toyota Prius v Five  Blue Ribbon Metallic exterior / Misty Gray interior This 2014 Toyota Prius v Five pairs efficient hybrid performance with generous cargo flexibility and thoughtful factory-equipped features. Powered by Toyotas 1.8L Hybrid I4 producing 134 hp (combined system output), the Prius v delivers excellent economy  EPA-rated at 44 MPG city and 40 MPG highway  and smooth, quiet operation thanks to the hybrid drivetrain and electronically controlled CVT. The exterior is finished in Blue Ribbon Metallic and the cabin is trimmed in Misty Gray. Overall condition is excellent, and the vehicle comes with a CARFAX report indicating a single owner. Factory-equipped features and highlights: - Hybrid Synergy Drive with 1.8L four-cylinder hybrid engine and electronic continuously variable transmission (E-CVT) for seamless power delivery and regenerative braking. - Fuel economy and driver aids: ECO and EV driving modes, multi-information display with fuel economy readouts, and energy flow indicators. - Infotainment and connectivity: Toyota Entune-compatible touchscreen infotainment with Bluetooth hands-free phone and audio streaming, USB and auxiliary inputs, and an integrated rearview camera for added convenience when parking. - Comfort and convenience: Keyless entry with push-button start, power windows and door locks, tilt-and-telescoping steering column, cruise control, automatic climate control, and heated front seats for added comfort. - Seating and cargo flexibility: Spacious five-passenger interior with rear 60/40 split-folding seats to expand cargo capacity, rear seatbacks fold flat to accommodate larger loads. - Exterior and utility: Stylish alloy wheels, roof rails for additional cargo-carrying capability, projector-style headlamps, and fog lights for improved visibility in poor conditions. - Safety and security: Comprehensive standard safety equipment including Anti-lock Braking System (ABS), Electronic Brake-force Distribution (EBD), Brake Assist, Vehicle Stability Control (VSC)/Traction Control, Smart Stop Technology, a full complement of airbags (front, side and curtain), and Tire Pressure Monitoring System (TPMS). - Quality and history: Excellent overall condition, one-owner vehicle with a clean CARFAX report. This Prius v Five offers a practical, fuel-efficient package with upscale conveniences and a versatile cargo area  ideal for drivers who want hybrid efficiency without sacrificing utility. 2014 Toyota Prius v Five  pintura exterior Blue Ribbon Metallic / interior Misty Gray Este Toyota Prius v Five 2014 combina un rendimiento h鱈brido eficiente con una gran versatilidad de carga y caracter鱈sticas de f叩brica bien equipadas. description: The 2013 Subaru Impreza WRX Premium Wagon is a sporty, practical hatchback blending rally-inspired performance with all-weather capability, featuring a 265-hp turbo BOXER engine, standard Symmetrical AWD, 5-speed manual, and premium features like leather, heated seats, and auto climate control, offering exciting thrills with daily utility and solid value for performance enthusiasts. Transmission: 5-speed manual transmission. Performance: Quick acceleration (0-60 mph in 5.3s in tests), sport-tuned suspension, and functional hood scoop. Premium Features: Leather upholstery, heated front seats, automatic climate control, Bluetooth, cruise control, and 17-inch alloy wheels. Body Style: Sport Wagon (hatchback) offers significant cargo versatility. What It Offers Rally Heritage: A direct connection to Subaru's legendary rally performance in a practical package. All-Weather Confidence: AWD provides stability and grip in diverse driving conditions. Balanced Performance: Exciting power without the extreme harshness of the higher-tier STI model. Utility: Ample cargo space for gear, groceries, or road trips.

description:
Introducing the 2013 Subaru Outback 2.5i Limited, the perfect combination of style, performance, and reliability. This versatile vehicle is equipped with a powerful 2.5L H4 engine, producing an impressive 173 horsepower and 174 ft. lbs. of torque. Paired with a smooth CVT transmission, this Outback offers a seamless driving experience.

Step inside and experience the luxurious and spacious interior of the 2.5i Limited. With plenty of legroom and premium leather seats, you and your passengers will be riding in comfort and style. The power-adjustable driver's seat and heated front seats add even more convenience and comfort to your driving experience.

Not only does this Outback offer a comfortable ride, but it also has impressive safety features. With Subaru's renowned Symmetrical All-Wheel Drive system, you can confidently navigate any road condition. The Limited trim also includes features such as a rearview camera, blind-spot detection, and automatic emergency braking, giving you peace of mind on every journey.

But the features don't stop there. The 2.5i Limited comes equipped with a power moonroof, dual-zone automatic climate control, and a premium Harman Kardon sound system, making every drive a luxurious one. Plus, with its roof rails and spacious cargo area, you can easily pack up for any adventure.

Don't miss your chance to own this 2013 Subaru Outback 2.5i Limited. With its sleek design, impressive performance, and advanced features, it's the perfect choice for anyone looking for a reliable and versatile vehicle. Come take a test drive and experience the Outback for yourself. Hurry, this one won't last long!

description:
The 2013 Toyota Prius v Five is a smart choice for drivers who want the efficiency of a hybrid with the added practicality of a larger wagon-style body. Unlike the standard Prius, the Prius v focuses on interior space and versatility, making it especially appealing for families, commuters, or anyone who needs extra cargo room without stepping into a full-size SUV.

On the road, the Prius v delivers a smooth and predictable driving experience, prioritizing comfort and fuel efficiency over aggressive performance. The hybrid system is quiet and refined, and its excellent fuel economy makes it ideal for long commutes and road trips alike. Steering is light and easy, which adds to its relaxed, stress-free character in city driving.

Inside, the Five trim offers a more premium feel, with higher-quality materials, comfortable seating, and a well-organized dashboard. The cabin is airy and spacious, providing ample legroom for passengers and a flexible cargo area that adapts easily to daily errands or weekend travel. Technology and safety features are straightforward and practical, reflecting Toyotas focus on usability and long-term reliability.

Overall, the 2013 Toyota Prius v Five stands out as a dependable, fuel-efficient vehicle that blends practicality with proven hybrid technology. For buyers looking for a comfortable, economical car with extra space and Toyotas well-earned reputation for durability, this Prius v Five remains a compelling option even years after its release.

ABOUT US: Rich's Cars is a family-run dealership that focuses on the customer first. Rich has been in the car business for 25 years and is experienced in providing excellent quality vehicles. You don't last in this business without treating people the right way. We offer a low-pressure buying experience, with salesman that act more like friends than vultures. All of our vehicles undergo thorough multi-point inspections to ensure they are mechanically sound. Have questions about our service? Check out our reviews! Give us a call or send us a text at 435-752-7424!
BRANDED TITLES: We sell rebuilt/restored vehicles because they offer superior value for our clients. All of our branded cars go through very rigorous and thorough testing. We oversee the build process to ensure our standards are met. We will NEVER sell a car that we feel has been structurally compromised or unsafe in any way. This means NO cut corners, NO safety issues. All branded cars go through 3 sets of eyes to ensure the best cars are being sold. Comes with a 3 month bumper to bumper warranty free-of-charge. Ask us what was repaired on them! BUY BRANDED to save thousands on your next car -- and get a better bang for your buck.
OUR WARRANTY: Bumper to bumper coverage for 3 months/3,000 miles is offered for all branded titles and cars under 100k miles. This covers any mechanical malfunction with the car following the purchase, with $0 deductible. We guarantee our cars because we trust them. We offer this same warranty coverage for up to 5 years at an additional cost. Our extended warranties are NOT 3rd party warranties, so there is no run-around in getting repairs covered. It is a personable, reasonable, and excellent service offered for convenience to our customers.
FINANCING: With a seasoned team of finance professionals, we have the knowledge and experience to get you the very best rate for your credit experience. Credit Union financing is located on location. We will never increase the price for outside financing, cash payments, or other arrangements. We offer competitive rates for financing and can regularly get interest rate discounts for you. You can apply for financing on our website at: https://www.richscarsncredit.c... (https://www.richscarsncredit.com/financing)
NATIONWIDE SHIPPING: At an additional cost, we can arrange shipping to anywhere in the continental United States. Reach out to us and we can provide an estimate for shipping. We regularly sell cars out of state, due to our service, inventory, and pricing.
NO BIG DEALER BS: $399 DOC FEE is the only dealership fee we have. Utah residents are subject to sales tax, and registration fees. We will never raise the price on a car for cash payment or outside financing.

Comfort, confidence, and capability come together in this 2013 Subaru Outback 2.5i Limited, a SUV built for drivers who want reliability with premium features. Finished in sleek Crystal Black Silica, this 4D Sport Utility delivers timeless styling paired with Subarus legendary AWD, giving you confidence in rain, snow, and changing road conditions. Recognized as a 2013 IIHS Top Safety Pick, this Outback reflects Subarus long-standing commitment to safety and durability. description: 2013 Toyota Prius v Two  Magnetic Gray Metallic exterior, Misty Gray cloth interior. Excellent overall condition. Below 129,000 miles (averaging under 10,000 miles per year). 1.8L Hybrid I4 with Toyota Hybrid Synergy Drive, rated at 134 hp combined. Excellent fuel economy: EPA-estimated 44 MPG city / 40 MPG highway. Key factory-standard features and equipment: - Powertrain and driving systems: 1.8L Atkinson-cycle four-cylinder paired with electric motor and CVT (electronically controlled continuously variable transmission), front-wheel drive, regenerative braking, selectable drive modes including EV/Normal/Eco to prioritize efficiency, standard stability control and traction control systems. - Performance and safety: Anti-lock braking system (ABS) with electronic brake-force distribution (EBD) and brake assist, multiple airbags (front, front side and side curtain), Tire Pressure Monitoring System (TPMS), LATCH child-seat anchors, daytime running lights. - Exterior: Magnetic Gray Metallic paint, aerodynamic liftback/wagon body with versatile rear cargo area, integrated roof rails for added utility, halogen projector headlights and alloy wheels (factory style). - Interior and comfort: Misty Gray cloth seating for five with manual seat adjustments, 60/40 split-folding rear seats to expand cargo capacity and create a flat loading floor for larger items, power windows and door locks, tilt-and-telescoping steering column, cruise control and intermittent windshield wipers, air conditioning with cabin filtration. - Convenience and connectivity: Toyota Entune audio system (factory configuration) with AM/FM radio, CD player, auxiliary input and USB connectivity, Bluetooth hands-free phone capability and audio streaming, steering-wheel-mounted audio and phone controls. - Practicality: Ample cargo space for the class with a low cargo sill and a configurable loading area, numerous cubbies and cupholders, rear privacy cover for cargo area. This Prius v Two offers the utility of a small wagon with the fuel efficiency of Toyotas hybrid system, making it well suited for daily commuting, family use, or anyone prioritizing fuel economy and practical cargo versatility. The exterior and interior colors are well matched and the vehicle presents in excellent condition throughout. Auto West 2110 Pine St. REDDING, CA 96001 (530) 243-9615

The 2013 Kia Soul Base is not just about looks and performance, it's a vehicle that has been recognized for its exceptional value and dependability. The Kia Soul has been highly praised in the automotive world, earning top spots in the J.D. The Kia Soul Base is a vehicle that stands out from the crowd, offering a blend of practicality and panache that few others can match. In summary, the 2013 Kia Soul Base is more than just a car, it's an experience waiting to be discovered. With its eye-catching red exterior, reliable performance, and award-winning pedigree, this hatchback is the perfect companion for those who value style, substance, and savings. Dont miss out on the opportunity to own a vehicle that combines cool with confidence. Come see it for yourself and take the first step towards driving a car that truly reflects who you are. The road is calling, and the Kia Soul Base is ready to take you there in style!

description:
Introducing the 2013 Subaru Outback 2.5i Limited - the perfect combination of style, comfort, and performance. This versatile crossover SUV is ready to take on any adventure with its powerful 2.5L H4 engine that delivers 173 horsepower and 174 ft. lbs. of torque. And with the smooth and efficient CVT transmission, you'll experience a seamless driving experience every time.

Step inside and you'll be greeted by a spacious and luxurious interior, complete with leather-trimmed seats and ample cargo space. The 2.5i Limited also comes equipped with a host of advanced features, including a premium sound system, Bluetooth connectivity, and a touchscreen display.

But the 2013 Subaru Outback 2.5i Limited is not just about comfort - it's also built for safety. With its advanced all-wheel drive system, you'll have enhanced traction and stability on any road surface. Plus, the Outback has earned top ratings in crash tests, giving you peace of mind on every journey.

Don't miss out on the opportunity to own this reliable and versatile 2013 Subaru Outback 2.5i Limited. Come take a test drive and experience its impressive performance and features for yourself. Hurry, this gem won't last long!

description:
Discover the exceptional value and versatility of this 2013 Toyota Venza Limited. With its sleek silver exterior, this well-appointed crossover offers a commanding presence on the road. Boasting a 3.5L V6 engine and front-wheel drive, the Venza delivers a dynamic and efficient driving experience, achieving an impressive 19 city/26 highway MPG.

Remote keyless entry
Traction control
ABS brakes
Low tire pressure warning
Electronic Stability Control
Heated door mirrors
Compass
Illuminated entry
Alloy wheels

Beyond its impressive performance, this Venza Limited is packed with a wealth of premium features that elevate your driving experience. Enjoy the comfort of dual-zone automatic climate control, the convenience of a power driver's seat, and the connectivity of steering wheel-mounted audio controls. The Venza's spacious interior and versatile cargo area make it the perfect companion for your everyday adventures and weekend getaways.

The Venza's safety is equally impressive, with a comprehensive suite of airbags, including front dual, side impact, and overhead units, as well as anti-whiplash front head restraints and an anti-roll bar for added protection. Brake assist and electronic stability control further enhance the Venza's road-holding capabilities, giving you the confidence to tackle any driving situation with ease.

Thoughtful details like the HomeLink garage door transmitter, auto-dimming rearview mirror, and illuminated entry ensure your comfort and convenience, while the 20-inch alloy wheels and body-color bumpers lend a touch of sophistication to the Venza's exterior.

This 2013 Toyota Venza Limited represents an exceptional value in the crossover market. With its impressive features, efficient performance, and comprehensive safety suite, it's the perfect blend of practicality and style. We invite you to experience the Venza's exceptional capabilities for yourself. Visit our showroom today and let us demonstrate how this exceptional vehicle can enhance your driving experience.

AWD

description:
Discover the versatile and stylish 2013 Kia Soul Base, a compact car that offers exceptional value and a host of impressive features. With its sleek exterior design and spacious interior, this Soul is the perfect companion for your urban adventures.

Carpeted Floor Mats

Slip into the driver's seat and experience the comfort of the woven cloth upholstery, complemented by the convenience of power windows, power steering, and remote keyless entry. Stay connected with the AM/FM/CD/MP3 audio system, complete with SiriusXM radio and steering wheel-mounted audio controls.

The 1.6L I4 DGI Gamma engine, paired with a 6-speed automatic transmission, delivers a smooth and efficient ride, with an impressive EPA-estimated 25 city/30 highway MPG. Enjoy the confidence of 4-wheel disc brakes, ABS, and electronic stability control, ensuring a safe and responsive driving experience.

Versatility is the hallmark of the 2013 Kia Soul Base. The split-folding rear seat allows you to easily accommodate your cargo needs, while the rear window wiper and variably intermittent wipers keep your visibility clear in any weather. Stay comfortable year-round with the air conditioning and rear window defroster.

Discover the perfect balance of style, technology, and practicality in the 2013 Kia Soul Base. This compact car is a true standout, offering an exceptional value proposition that is sure to impress. Schedule a test drive today and experience the joy of owning this remarkable vehicle.

Discover the perfect balance of capability and comfort in this 2013 Subaru Outback 2.5i Premium. This versatile crossover SUV is ready to elevate your driving experience with its impressive array of features and exceptional performance.

Powered by a 2.5L 4-Cylinder DOHC 16V engine and equipped with Subaru's renowned Symmetrical All-Wheel Drive system, this Outback delivers a confident and capable driving experience, whether you're navigating city streets or exploring the great outdoors. With an impressive EPA-estimated 24 mpg in the city and 30 mpg on the highway, this Outback strikes the perfect balance between performance and efficiency.

Slip behind the wheel and you'll be greeted by a host of premium features, including a power driver's seat, heated front seats, and a premium audio system with steering wheel-mounted controls. The spacious and versatile interior offers ample room for passengers and cargo, with a split-folding rear seat that allows you to easily accommodate your unique needs.

Safety is also a top priority, with features like dual front airbags, side-impact airbags, and electronic stability control ensuring your peace of mind on the road. The Outback's all-weather capabilities are further enhanced by the included All-Weather Package, which adds a windshield wiper de-icer, heated exterior mirrors, and more to help you conquer any driving conditions.

Whether you're looking for a reliable daily driver, a capable adventure companion, or a family-friendly SUV, this 2013 Subaru Outback 2.5i Premium is an exceptional choice. With its impressive list of features, impressive performance, and uncompromising Subaru quality, it's a vehicle that's sure to exceed your expectations. Visit our showroom today and experience the difference for yourself.

Discover the versatility and capability of the 2012 Subaru Outback 2.5i Premium. This exceptional all-wheel-drive wagon is the perfect companion for your adventures, offering a seamless blend of performance, comfort, and advanced features.

Equipped with a 2.5L 4-cylinder SOHC 16V engine paired with a CVT Lineartronic transmission, the Outback delivers a responsive and efficient driving experience. Boasting an impressive 22 city/29 highway MPG, this Subaru will help you go the distance without sacrificing fuel economy.

Subaru's commitment to safety is evident in the Outback's comprehensive suite of features, including ABS brakes, dual front airbags, and electronic stability control. You can drive with confidence, knowing your Outback is engineered to keep you and your passengers secure.

Experience the perfect blend of capability, comfort, and style in the 2012 Subaru Outback 2.5i Premium. Visit our showroom today and let us demonstrate how this exceptional vehicle can enhance your driving experience.

Discover the perfect blend of style, technology, and efficiency with this exceptional 2023 Kia Soul LX. This sleek and versatile compact SUV is ready to elevate your driving experience and meet the demands of your modern lifestyle.

Boasting a comprehensive list of desirable features, this Soul LX is equipped to exceed your expectations. Enjoy the convenience of Apple CarPlay and Android Auto, stay connected with the built-in Wi-Fi hotspot, and let the Blind-Spot Collision-Avoidance Assist and Rear Cross-Traffic Collision Avoidance Assist systems provide an extra layer of safety and confidence on the road. The Lane Change Assist feature further enhances your awareness, while the 16-inch alloy wheels add a touch of style.

New Tires Installed

This well-maintained Soul LX has been meticulously cared for, with just 85,757 miles on the odometer. The Illuminated Scuff Plates, Carpeted Floor Mats, and Standard Mudguards add a touch of refinement, while the Envelope Cargo Net helps you stay organized.

Beyond the impressive list of features, this Soul LX also boasts a one-owner history, ensuring a reliable and well-cared-for vehicle. With its stylish exterior, comfortable interior, and advanced technology, this Kia Soul LX is the perfect companion for your daily commute, weekend adventures, and everything in between.

Don't miss your chance to experience the exceptional value and versatility of this 2023 Kia Soul LX. Contact us today to schedule a test drive and discover why this compact SUV should be your next automotive investment.

description: ```html  2023 KIA Soul LX Wagon for Sale at Superstar Motorz in Milwaukie, Clackamas, Oregon   Why Choose the 2023 KIA Soul LX Wagon? Looking for a vehicle that combines bold design, exceptional performance, and everyday practicality? The 2023 KIA Soul LX Wagon is the perfect choice. Available now at Superstar Motorz in Milwaukie, Clackamas, Oregon, this stylish and versatile wagon is ideal for those who demand more from their daily drive. Whether you're commuting to work, running errands, or heading out on an adventure, the KIA Soul LX is ready to exceed your expectations.   Eye-Catching Exterior Design of the 2023 KIA Soul The 2023 KIA Soul LX Wagon stands out from the crowd with its unique and modern design. Its boxy shape, bold lines, and striking front grille make it instantly recognizable on the road. The compact yet spacious design ensures that you get the best of both worlds - urban-friendly dimensions with ample interior space. The sleek headlights and stylish taillights add a touch of sophistication, while the aerodynamic profile enhances fuel efficiency and overall performance.   Comfortable and Functional Interior of the 2023 KIA Soul LX Step inside the 2023 KIA Soul LX Wagon and experience a world of comfort and convenience. The thoughtfully designed interior offers plenty of headroom and legroom for both the driver and passengers. The high-quality materials and ergonomic layout ensure a comfortable ride, even on long journeys. With its versatile seating configuration and ample cargo space, the KIA Soul LX is perfect for families, road trips, and everything in between.   Performance That Inspires Confidence Under the hood, the 2023 KIA Soul LX Wagon is powered by a reliable 2.0L I4 engine that delivers 147 horsepower and 132 lb-ft of torque. This front-wheel-drive (FWD) vehicle is paired with an automatic transmission, ensuring a smooth and responsive driving experience. Whether you're navigating city streets or cruising on the highway, the KIA Soul LX provides the perfect balance of power and efficiency. Its agile handling and precise steering make every drive enjoyable and stress-free.   Advanced Technology Features in the 2023 KIA Soul LX The 2023 KIA Soul LX Wagon is equipped with a range of advanced technology features designed to enhance your driving experience. The intuitive infotainment system keeps you connected and entertained with seamless smartphone integration, Bluetooth connectivity, and a user-friendly touchscreen display. Stay in control with features like steering wheel-mounted audio controls and voice recognition. With the KIA Soul LX, staying connected on the go has never been easier.   Safety Comes First in the 2023 KIA Soul LX Wagon Your safety is a top priority in the 2023 KIA Soul LX. This wagon is equipped with a suite of safety features designed to keep you and your passengers protected on the road. From advanced airbags and anti-lock braking systems to electronic stability control and tire pressure monitoring, the KIA Soul LX has you covered. Drive with confidence, knowing that your vehicle is designed to help prevent accidents and protect you in the event of an emergency.   Fuel Efficiency That Saves You Money The 2023 KIA Soul LX Wagon is not only fun to drive but also economical. Its efficient 2.0L engine ensures that you get excellent fuel economy, making it a great choice for daily commutes and long road trips alike. Spend less time at the pump and more time enjoying the open road with the KIA Soul LX. It's a practical and budget-friendly option for drivers who want to save money without sacrificing performance.   Practicality Meets Style in the 2023 KIA Soul LX The 2023 KIA Soul LX Wagon is designed with practicality in mind, without compromising on style. Its compact size makes it easy to maneuver in tight spaces, while the spacious interior and versatile cargo area provide plenty of room for all your gear. Whether you're loading up groceries, packing for a weekend getaway, or transporting larger items, the KIA Soul LX has the space and flexibility to meet your needs. It's the perfect blend of form and function.   Visit Superstar Motorz in Milwaukie, Clackamas, Oregon Today Ready to experience the 2023 KIA Soul LX Wagon for yourself? Visit Superstar Motorz in Milwaukie, Clackamas, Oregon, and take this incredible vehicle for a test drive. Our friendly and knowledgeable team is here to help you find the perfect car to suit your lifestyle and budget. Don't miss your chance to own this stylish, versatile, and high-performing vehicle. Stop by today and discover why the 2023 KIA Soul LX is the ideal choice for your next car.   息 2023 Superstar Motorz. All rights reserved. Located in Milwaukie, Clackamas, Oregon. ```

      • Forward collision mitigation - Forward thinking. You look away for just a second and suddenly the vehicle in front of you has stopped. That's when the forward collision mitigation system comes to life. When it senses an impending impact, it will activate a combination of features to help prevent or reduce the severity of an accident. Forward collision mitigation is always looking ahead.

This system constantly monitors the road ahead to identify and track pedestrians. It projects that image to an interior display screen, AND should an impact become likely, Pedestrian impact prevention takes steps to avoid a collision.

description:
Discover the perfect blend of capability, comfort, and technology in this stunning 2017 Subaru Outback 3.6R Limited. With its impressive 3.6L Boxer H6 DOHC 24V engine, Lineartronic CVT transmission, and Symmetrical All-Wheel Drive, this Outback delivers exceptional performance and confidence on the road.

Standout features include:
EyeSight & Navigation & High Beam Assist & RAB
Navigation System
Popular Package #5

This Outback is also equipped with a host of advanced safety and convenience technologies, including Reverse Auto Brake, Adaptive Cruise Control, and the Subaru STARLINK 7.0" Multimedia Navigation System with voice-activated controls, Bluetooth connectivity, and SiriusXM capabilities.

Inside, you'll find a spacious and well-appointed cabin with perforated leather-trimmed upholstery, heated front and rear seats, a power driver's seat, and a panoramic moonroof. The Harman Kardon premium audio system with 12 speakers ensures an immersive listening experience.

With its impressive 20 city/27 highway MPG ratings, this Outback offers exceptional efficiency and practicality. The generous cargo space and standard roof rails make it the perfect companion for your active lifestyle, whether you're embarking on a road trip or tackling your daily commute.

Discover the perfect blend of capability, comfort, and technology in this exceptional 2017 Subaru Outback 3.6R Limited. Experience the difference for yourself and schedule a test drive today. We're confident you'll be impressed by this outstanding vehicle.

Germain Subaru of Columbus-614-347-6450 1395 Auto Mall Pkwy, Columbus, OH 43228.

description:
Discover the perfect blend of style, convenience, and performance with this 2017 Kia Soul Base. This versatile compact car is ready to elevate your daily commute and weekend adventures.

Boasting a sleek gray exterior, this Kia Soul combines a bold, eye-catching design with practical functionality. Slip behind the wheel and you'll be greeted by a well-appointed interior, featuring:

SiriusXM radio
Steering wheel-mounted audio controls
6-way adjustable driver's seat
Alloy wheels

The 2.0L I4 engine and 6-speed automatic transmission with Sportmatic provide a smooth, responsive driving experience, while the front-wheel-drive system ensures confident handling, no matter the road conditions. With an EPA-estimated 25 city/30 highway MPG, this Kia Soul delivers impressive fuel efficiency to help you save at the pump.

Comfort and convenience are at the forefront, with features like air conditioning, power windows, and remote keyless entry. The split-folding rear seats and available cargo tray provide ample space for all your gear, making this Kia Soul the perfect companion for your active lifestyle.

Safety is also a top priority, with a comprehensive suite of advanced safety technologies, including airbags, anti-lock brakes, and electronic stability control. You can drive with confidence, knowing you and your passengers are well-protected.

This 2017 Kia Soul Base represents an exceptional value in the compact car segment. With its stylish design, impressive features, and efficient performance, it's the perfect choice for those seeking a versatile and practical vehicle. Experience the difference for yourself schedule a test drive today and discover the joy of driving a Kia Soul.

2017 Subaru Outback 3.6R Limited
Wilderness Green Metallic | 139,251 Miles | Survivor of Roads, Trails, and Probably Your Exs Drama

This 2017 Subaru Outback 3.6R Limited in Wilderness Green Metallic has 139,251 miles, which in Subaru speak means: Ive seen things and Im still ready for more.

Its basically the ultimate road trip buddy:

Has survived every winter storm that dared to exist

Probably drank three thermoses of coffee on early morning commutes

Knows the backroads better than Google Maps

The Limited trim brings leather, tech, and luxury touches because just surviving the apocalypse isnt enough, you also want to be comfortable while doing it.

This Outback is perfect for:

Adventurers who need room for bikes, skis, dogs, or all three simultaneously

People who like cars that silently judge lesser SUVs in parking lots

Anyone who appreciates a green SUV that screams, I mean business but Im chill about it

139k miles? Thats not old. Thats battle-tested legend status.

This Outback doesnt just drive.
It hikes, hauls, and probably drinks less coffee than you do.

Tim Dahle Mazda Murray
801-290-0014
www.timdahlemazdamurray.com

description: The 2017 Volkswagen Golf Alltrack Wagon 4D SEL AWD blends practicality, efficiency, and European style into a versatile package perfect for daily driving and weekend adventures. Powered by a responsive 1.8L turbocharged engine and paired with a smooth automatic transmission, it delivers confident acceleration while maintaining excellent fuel economy. The 4MOTION all-wheel-drive system enhances traction and stability, making this wagon well suited for changing road conditions. Inside, the SEL trim offers an upscale feel with premium materials, comfortable seating, and thoughtful design throughout the cabin. The interior is spacious and flexible, providing generous cargo room with the rear seats folded down, ideal for road trips, outdoor gear, or everyday errands. Modern technology features add convenience and connectivity, helping make every drive more enjoyable. With its refined ride quality, distinctive wagon styling, and reputation for solid German engineering, the Golf Alltrack stands out as a smart, capable, and enjoyable vehicle for drivers who want more than the ordinary.

2017 Subaru Impreza Premium | Clean Title | No Accidents
This 2017 Subaru Impreza Premium is a clean, well-maintained vehicle with a clean title and no accident history. It has a strong service history and has clearly been taken care of. Subaru s symmetrical all-wheel drive makes this Impreza extremely capable in all weather conditions while still delivering excellent fuel economy and a comfortable ride.

The interior is clean and comfortable with a well-laid-out cabin that s easy to live with day to day. Smooth steering, solid handling, and Subaru reliability make this an ideal daily driver, commuter, or first car.
Overall, this Impreza is dependable, practical, and ready to be driven with confidence.

It's Only a Great Deal If It's a Great Vehicle!

Welcome to Car Connection of Bedford!

Were thrilled that your search has led you to us! As a trusted dealership located in Bedford, Ohio, just outside Cleveland, we cater to customers nationwide. If youre not from our area, no worries! We sell and ship our vehicles, usually within a few days, anywhere in the country. Car Connection of Bedford is a family-owned and operated business committed to providing top-quality vehicles and exceptional customer service.

Why Choose Car Connection of Bedford?

Hand-Picked Selection: We hand-pick every car, truck, and SUV, searching the entire country for only the nicest vehicles that we can sell for below market prices. Youll find outstanding quality without breaking the bank!
Best Value Research: To find the best value, we do the research before you do. We strive to provide you with the best value on every vehicle. Our success is due to being a highly customer-centric dealership.

Lower Prices for You: Being a small business with lower overhead costs means we can pass the savings on to you! Enjoy unbeatable prices on our premium vehicles without compromising on quality.

Rigorous Safety Inspections: Rest assured knowing that all vehicles pass our vigorous and detailed safety inspection, ensuring you drive away in a safe and reliable car.

Trusted Source: Our commitment to quality and customer satisfaction makes us your go-to source for premium vehicles.

Check Out Our Reviews: Dont just take our word for it! Explore our glowing reviews on Google that testify to our dedication to customer satisfaction.

Unbeatable Deals Await You: Discover why Car Connection of Bedford sells moreour prices and service are unmatched!

Fast, Fun, and Easy Car Buying

At Car Connection of Bedford, we believe that buying a car should be an enjoyable experience. Whether you choose to call, click, or stop by, we'll show you just how fast, fun, and easy it is to drive away in the car of your dreams!
Family-Owned, Customer-Friendly

When you choose us, you're not just buying a car, you're becoming part of our family. As a customer-friendly, family-owned company, we prioritize your satisfaction and trust.

Need Credit? We Can Help!

Apply for financing on our secure website to get pre-approved. Our team will guide you through all your options, ensuring you secure the best financing package that fits your needs.

Out of Town Buyers? No Problem!

Car Connection of Bedford can assist with delivery, pick-up, and travel arrangements, making the car-buying process seamlessno matter where you are!

Ready to Experience the Car Connection of Bedford Difference?

Call us now at (216) 929-7826 or apply for financing online. Let us show you why we're the preferred choice for car buyers looking for unbeatable deals and exceptional service.

Car Connection of BedfordFast, Fun, and Easy!

description:
Colorado's top choice for pre-owned Subaru's for over 32 years. No junk here. Same ownership the whole time. We are committed to providing the best cars for your money by performing professional service, repairs, and the overall best quality at any given price point. We've done it for over 32 years, others can't come close to what we offer.
Call or Text 720-738-4605 JapaneseCarConnection.com Located at 1245 South Kalamath St., Denver CO 80223, open M-F 10-6, Sat 10-5, Closed Sundays.
All cars come with receipts and work orders of the work that we performed. We do a lot of repair work to our cars to ensure that you get the best value for your money. We start out by selecting cars that are in great condition and then put it through a 120 point inspection to determine what maintenance the car needs. Here we have a 2017 Subaru Outback 2.5i Premium, 127k, Non smoking, Non pet. Mechanically, this is a very sound vehicle. We just resealed the transmission pump, New Valve Cover Gaskets, New spark plugs, CVT transmission fluid service, NEW differential fluid service, NEW rear brake pads & rotors, New filters and oil change. This Outback boasts the ever so popular Crystal White pearl paint with the highly desired heated black cloth interior.
3 Month/3000 Mile Warranty included on all cars! We offer quick and Easy Financing options, zero to low down Payment options available with approved credit. Trade ins are welcome.
What sets us apart from other dealers:
1. Japanese Car Connection is a Carfax advantage dealer with free car fax reports visit, japanesecarconnection.com.
2. All vehicles receive a 120 point inspection by our mechanics at our facility
3. Japanese Car Connection has sold over 10,000 cars and performed over 3000 Subaru head gasket jobs
4. We road test all of our cars and perform more services to our cars than the competition
5. Japanese Car Connection is very well established and has been at the same location since 1985
6. Japanese Car Connection provides A nationwide 3 month/3,000 mile warranty on the cars we sell.
7. Receipts and work orders available on request
We encourage you to buy from a dealership with a long standing record that has stood the test of time. Not many dealers can say they have the longevity matching Japanese Car Connection
We always strive for quality in the cars we sell and do not believe in ever cutting corners. Starting as a humble little place in the previous owner's garage in 1978 as Honda Menders, Japanese Car Connection has evolved into one of the top specialized used car dealerships around, eventually moving to our current location in 1985. In 1993, ownership changed to our current owner and we have been proud to serve Colorado and our surrounding area for over 40 years, specializing in servicing and selling Subaru's, Honda's/Acura's and Toyota's/Lexus. We have many Subaru's, Honda's and Toyota's to choose from, go to japanesecarconnection.com to see our current inventory.

This Titanium Gray 2017 Kia Soul Base is a great choice! Check out the following: One Owner! City 25/Hwy 30 Convenience Package ($500 value)
    Wheel Locks ($55 value)
      Carpeted Floor Mats ($120 value)
        TITANIUM GRAY, BLACK, CLOTH SEAT TRIM, CONVENIENCE PACKAGE, WHEEL LOCKS, CARPETED FLOOR MATS Convenience
        • Cruise control with steering wheel mounted controls. Set it and forget it. Road trips used to be stressful, until cruise control set the pace. Simply set the desired speed using the steering wheel mounted controls and it will maintain that speed without driver intervention. This can help minimize driver fatigue and improve overall fuel economy. Resting your right foot is right at your fingertips thanks to cruise control with steering wheel mounted controls.
        • Mechanical
        In-car Entertainment
        • Wireless audio streaming - Strike the cord. With wireless streaming, the endless library of music on your mobile device is available through your vehicle's sound system! Make a playlist befitting of your road trip as it rolls along, let the back seat passengers control the selection, catch up on your favorite podcasts. With wireless audio streaming, all you have to do is press play.
        • External memory control - Digital access anywhere. Your media of choice doesn't have to stay behind just because you're going somewhere. Now, music and media from your hard-drive, devices or memory stick are easy to access and control from your vehicle, thanks to the external memory control.
        Powertrain and Mechanical
        • Variable valve timing - Change your output. There are a lot of variables in your drive, so why should your engine always operate the same? With variable valve timing, the engine is efficient at both low and high RPM's, so you get better fuel efficiency, cleaner emissions and improved performance. Variable valve timing provides a better drive, every time.
        • Inline-4 engines produce adequate horsepower while typically offering better fuel efficiency and more economical maintenance than larger engines.
        Safety and Security
        • Brake assist - Stop right there. Something jumps out into the middle of the road and you need to stop now! With brake assist, you will. It uses the speed of the brake pedal's travel to sense panic braking, then applies all available power to boost your stopping power. Brake assist can stop the accident before it is one.
        • Electronic stability control - Helping you stay grounded. By monitoring and comparing vehicle dynamics to driver input, this system acts instantly to help control the vehicle if it loses traction. It engages the traction control and anti-lock brake systems if skidding is detected, and it may even react well before you're aware of a loss of traction. With electronic stability control you can stay on the road ahead.
        • Hill hold control - Don't go back. You know the feeling - you're stopped on a hill and you're worried about your vehicle rolling backwards when you release the brakes. This is even more worrisome when you're towing. With hill hold control, the vehicle automatically applies brake force to prevent itself from rolling back. So whether you're towing a heavy load or simply stopped on a steep incline, hill hold control keeps you on the up and up.
        Technology and Telematics
        • Wireless connectivity - Strike the cord. Wireless technology makes it easy to place calls without having to fumble with your phone. It integrates your device with the system inside your vehicle for hands-free access. Keep connected and keep your hands on the wheel with wireless connectivity.

Introducing the 2017 Subaru Impreza Sport, the perfect combination of style, performance, and reliability. This sleek sedan is equipped with a powerful 2.0L 4-cylinder engine, capable of delivering an impressive 152 horsepower. But don't let its sporty exterior fool you, the Impreza Sport is also fuel-efficient, making it the ideal choice for both city and highway driving.

Step inside and experience the spacious and comfortable interior, designed with premium materials and advanced technology. The Impreza Sport boasts a 6.5-inch touchscreen display, Bluetooth connectivity, and a rearview camera for added convenience and safety. Plus, with its symmetrical all-wheel drive system, this car offers exceptional handling and traction in all weather conditions.

But that's not all, the 2017 Impreza Sport also comes with a host of impressive features such as a power moonroof, heated front seats, and a 6-speaker audio system. And with its generous cargo space, you'll have plenty of room for all your gear and essentials.

Don't miss your chance to own this stunning 2017 Subaru Impreza Sport. With its eye-catching design and unbeatable performance, it's the perfect choice for anyone looking for a reliable and stylish car. Visit our showroom today and take a test drive to truly experience the greatness of the 2017 Impreza Sport. Don't wait, drive away in your dream car today!

Boasting a sleek brown exterior and a well-appointed interior, this Soul Plus is more than just a practical commuter car. It's a true expression of your personal style. Highlighted features include:

Leather-wrapped steering wheel and shift knob
Heated front seats and steering wheel
Leatherette-wrapped instrument panel and door accents
Satin chrome interior door handles
Wireless charging for your compatible devices
Powerful Harman Kardon audio system with SiriusXM

The Soul Plus also delivers impressive efficiency, with an EPA-estimated 25 city/30 highway MPG. Its 6-speed automatic transmission with Sportmatic provides a smooth, responsive driving experience, while the front-wheel-drive system ensures confident handling in a variety of conditions.

Safety is paramount, and this Soul Plus comes equipped with a wealth of advanced features, including a backup camera, blind spot monitoring, and a suite of airbags to protect you and your passengers.

Whether you're commuting to the office or embarking on a weekend adventure, this 2017 Kia Soul Plus is the perfect companion. Its unique blend of style, technology, and efficiency make it a standout in the compact car segment.

We invite you to experience the joy of driving this exceptional vehicle for yourself. Schedule a test drive today and discover why the Kia Soul Plus is the perfect fit for your lifestyle.

description:
The 2017 MINI Cooper S Clubman is a premium compact wagon that blends iconic MINI styling with enhanced practicality, sporty performance, and distinctive design. It offers more cargo space and passenger comfort than the standard Cooper hatchback while keeping the funtodrive character that MINI is known for.

Performance & Driving Dynamics

Engine: The Cooper S Clubman is powered by a 2.0liter turbocharged fourcylinder engine, delivering lively acceleration and engaging performance.

Horsepower & Torque: The turbocharged engine produces strong output for its class, giving the vehicle a spirited feel in everyday driving and on winding roads.

Transmission: Buyers can choose between a 6speed manual transmission for more direct engagement or an available automatic transmission for smooth, convenient shifting.

Handling: True to MINI heritage, the Clubman offers responsive steering and agile handling, making it enjoyable to drive in city traffic and on open roads.

Interior & Comfort

Seating: The cabin comfortably seats five passengers, with supportive seats designed for both short trips and longer journeys.

Materials: Quality materials and unique design cues create a premium feel, with contrast stitching and stylish trim elements that reflect MINIs attention to detail.

Space & Practicality: The Clubmans wagon body style gives it more cargo room than typical hatchbacks. The split rear doors (barnstyle) open wide for easy loading of luggage, groceries, or gear.

Technology & Convenience

Infotainment: A central display often circular in design as a MINI signature provides access to audio, navigation (when equipped), and vehicle settings.

Connectivity: Standard connectivity features support smartphone use for music, calls, and navigation on the go.

Driver Ease: Controls are intuitive and within easy reach, emphasizing convenience and usability.

Safety & Driver Assistance

The Clubman includes a suite of safety features designed to help protect occupants and support confident driving. Common features may include front and side airbags, stability control, antilock brakes, and a rearview camera. Additional driver assistance options may be available depending on equipment.

Exterior Design

Signature Style: The 2017 Cooper S Clubman carries MINIs distinctive aesthetic with a wide stance, rounded headlights, and bold accents.

Unique Doors: The split rear barn doors are a hallmark of the Clubman model, enhancing cargo access and adding character.

Wheels & Trim: Stylish alloy wheels and available contrasting roof colors amplify the vehicles individual style.

Summary

The 2017 MINI Cooper S Clubman is a sporty, stylish compact wagon that offers:

Turbocharged performance with engaging handling

Comfortable seating for five passengers

Greater cargo versatility than a standard hatchback

Premium interior design with thoughtful details

Distinctive MINI styling and personality

description: 2017 Subaru Outback 2.5i Limited Overview This 2017 Subaru Outback 2.5i Limited is finished in Ice Silver Metallic and is powered by Subarus 2.5-liter horizontally opposed (H4) engine producing 175 hp and 174 lb-ft of torque. It is equipped with Subarus continuously variable transmission (CVT) and Symmetrical All-Wheel Drive. EPA fuel economy is rated at 25 MPG city and 32 MPG highway. The vehicle is in excellent overall condition, has a clean CARFAX report, and shows one previous owner. Performance and drivetrain - 2.5L H4 boxer engine  175 hp / 174 lb-ft torque - Continuously Variable Transmission (Lineartronic CVT) - Symmetrical All-Wheel Drive for consistent traction in varied conditions - Suspension tuned for a balanced ride and stability, with higher ground clearance than a typical passenger sedan for light off-road capability Exterior - Ice Silver Metallic paint - Distinctive Outback body cladding and lower-side protective panels - Roof rails designed to accept crossbars and cargo accessories for bikes, skis, or a cargo box - Fog lights and projector-style headlamps (factory Limited-level lighting package) - Alloy wheels (factory Limited wheels) Interior and comfort - Leather-trimmed seating surfaces (factory Limited feature) - Heated front seats for added comfort in cooler climates - Power-adjustable drivers seat with lumbar support - Split-folding 60/40 rear seat for flexible cargo and passenger arrangements - Dual-zone automatic climate control to maintain separate front temperature settings - Spacious cargo area with flat load floor and convenient tie-downs Technology and convenience - Keyless access with push-button start (factory Limited convenience feature) - Multi-function steering wheel with audio and cruise controls - Subaru STARLINK infotainment system with touchscreen (Bluetooth hands-free phone and audio streaming) - AM/FM stereo, USB and auxiliary inputs - Rearview camera for easier reversing and parking - Multiple 12V power outlets and available USB charging Safety - Standard safety systems including anti-lock brakes (ABS), vehicle dynamics control/stability control, and traction control - Front, side and curtain airbags for occupant protection - Tire pressure monitoring system - Rearview camera (standard on Limited) - Built to Subarus safety-focused engineering standards, some vehicles may be equipped with EyeSight driver-assist features (adaptive cruise control, pre-collision braking, lane departure warning) depending on factory options Condition and history - Excellent overall condition, both mechanically and cosmetically - Clean CARFAX report with no reported accidents - Single-owner history as indicated on the CARFAX This Outback combines Subarus all-weather capability and practical cargo versatility with Limited-level creature comforts and convenience features. For specific option confirmation (navigation, Harman/Kardon audio, EyeSight package, interior color), please request the vehicles window sticker or dealer option list to verify factory-installed options and interior finish. ULTIMATE MOTOR CARS 2101 Ogden Ave. Downers Grove, IL 60515 (630) 515-9595

description:
Experience the perfect blend of capability, technology, and style with this 2017 Subaru Outback 2.5i Limited. This versatile SUV is ready to take on any adventure, whether you're tackling the daily commute or exploring the great outdoors.

Highlighted features include:
EYESIGHT & NAVIGATION & HBA & RAB & HID LIGHTS
Subaru Starlink 7.0" Multimedia Navigation System
Aha
Harman/Kardon Surround Sound Speaker System
Power Liftgate
Adaptive Cruise Control
Reverse Auto Brake
Heated Reclining Front Bucket Seats

The Outback's 2.5L 4-cylinder DOHC engine paired with a CVT Lineartronic transmission delivers an exceptional balance of power and efficiency, with an EPA-estimated 25 city/32 highway MPG. Subaru's renowned Symmetrical All-Wheel Drive system ensures confident handling and traction in all conditions, making this Outback a true adventurer's companion.

Step inside and you'll be greeted by a wealth of premium features, including perforated leather-trimmed upholstery, a power driver's seat, and a dual-zone automatic climate control system. The Subaru Starlink infotainment system with navigation, Apple CarPlay, and Android Auto integration keeps you connected and entertained on the go.

Safety is a top priority in the Outback, with Subaru's advanced EyeSight driver-assist technology, High Beam Assist, and Reverse Auto Brake providing an extra layer of protection. The sleek exterior design with 18-inch alloy wheels and a power moonroof adds a touch of sophistication to this capable SUV.

Whether you're looking to conquer the great outdoors or simply enjoy a comfortable and connected driving experience, this 2017 Subaru Outback 2.5i Limited is the perfect choice. Visit us today to take it for a test drive and discover the exceptional value and versatility it has to offer.

Please visit us at 150 Manchester St Concord NH, 03301 or call us at (603)225-0200. Family owned & operated. Purchases include lifetime New Hampshire State Inspections. Use of complimentary service loaner fleet.

Introducing the 2017 Volkswagen Golf Alltrack TSI SEL 4Motion - the ultimate combination of style, performance, and versatility. This sleek and sophisticated vehicle is designed to take on any terrain with its advanced 4Motion all-wheel drive system. Whether you're navigating through city streets or embarking on an off-road adventure, the Golf Alltrack has got you covered.

Under the hood, you'll find a powerful and efficient TSI engine, providing the perfect balance of power and fuel efficiency. With its smooth and responsive handling, you'll enjoy a dynamic driving experience like no other. Plus, the SEL trim level offers top-of-the-line features such as a panoramic sunroof, premium audio system, and a navigation system to elevate your driving experience.

Step inside the spacious and luxurious interior, and you'll be greeted with premium materials and modern amenities. With ample head and legroom, the Golf Alltrack can comfortably accommodate up to five passengers, making it the perfect vehicle for family road trips or daily commutes.

But that's not all, the Golf Alltrack also boasts an impressive cargo capacity, thanks to its versatile hatchback design. Whether you need to transport groceries, sports equipment, or camping gear, the Golf Alltrack has got you covered with its ample storage space.

Don't miss your chance to own the 2017 Volkswagen Golf Alltrack TSI SEL 4Motion. Come take a test drive and experience the ultimate in performance, style, and versatility today!

Comfort, confidence, and versatility come together in this 2017 Subaru Outback 2.5i Limited, a SUV designed to handle everyday life with ease while keeping you comfortable on every mile. Finished in elegant Crystal White Pearl, this 4D Sport Utility delivers a refined look paired with Subarus legendary AWD, giving you sure-footed confidence in all road and weather conditions. Powered by a dependable 2.5L 4-Cylinder DOHC 16V engine, the Outback offers smooth, efficient performance perfect for commuting, family trips, and weekend adventures.

Step inside and enjoy a thoughtfully designed interior featuring slate black perforated leather-trimmed upholstery that adds a premium touch to an already spacious cabin. Known for its quiet ride and excellent visibility, the Outback is built for long drives and daily comfort alike. Subarus commitment to safety and reliability shines through in its long list of accolades, including 2017 IIHS Top Safety Pick+, KBB.com 12 Best Family Cars, 10 Most Comfortable Cars Under $30,000, and multiple Best All-Wheel-Drive and Residual Value awards. Honors for 5-Year Cost to Own and Brand Image further reinforce why the Outback remains one of the smartest SUV choices on the road.

With its flexible cargo space, proven durability, and reputation for long-term dependability, this Outback Limited is ready to support your next chapterwhether that means road trips, carpools, or everyday errands.

You can buy this 2017 Subaru Outback 2.5i Limited today at Ferguson Superstore in Broken Arrow, OK 74012.
At Ferguson, we are Upfront and Simple. We offer our best price to everyone, the first time, so you can enjoy a transparent, stress-free buying experience from start to finish.

description:
Discover the perfect blend of capability, style, and convenience with the 2017 Volkswagen Golf Alltrack TSI SE 4Motion. This versatile and well-equipped crossover is the ideal companion for your active lifestyle, offering an exceptional driving experience and a host of premium features.

Highlighted by its sleek, black exterior, the Golf Alltrack boasts a commanding presence on the road. Step inside and you'll be greeted by a wealth of premium amenities, including:

LED daytime running lights
Panoramic sunroof
Keyless entry and push-button start
Bluetooth connectivity
Fender premium audio system
Apple CarPlay and Android Auto integration
Rearview and backup cameras

The Golf Alltrack's turbocharged 1.8-liter engine and 6-speed DSG automatic transmission with Tiptronic provide a thrilling and efficient driving experience, delivering 170 horsepower and an impressive 30 MPG on the highway. Coupled with Volkswagen's 4MOTION all-wheel-drive system, this crossover is ready to tackle any road or weather condition with confidence.

Beyond its impressive performance, the Golf Alltrack is packed with a host of advanced safety features, including anti-lock brakes, electronic stability control, and a comprehensive airbag system. You can drive with peace of mind, knowing you and your passengers are well-protected.

Blending style, capability, and technology, the 2017 Volkswagen Golf Alltrack TSI SE 4Motion is the perfect choice for the discerning driver who demands more from their vehicle. Experience the difference for yourself and schedule a test drive today.

AutoNation Subaru Hilton Head is honored to present a wonderful example of pure vehicle design... this 2017 Subaru Outback Limited only has 103,076mi on it and could potentially be the vehicle of your dreams! If you're in the market for an incredible SUV -- and value on-the-road comfort and manners more than ultimate off-road prowess or tow capacity -- you'll definitely want to check out this Subaru Outback Limited. The impressive Subaru fuel-efficiency will make you quickly realize what you've been missing out on in life. It's noteworthy fuel economy and minimal emissions make this vehicle's value a cut above the rest.Navigate through all the icky weather with ease in this AWD-equipped Subaru Outback, and even get non-stop traction for your non-stop lifestyle! In addition to the amazing traction control, you may even qualify for an insurance reduction with this AWD vehicle. It's not often you find just the vehicle you are looking for AND with low mileage. This is your chance to take home a pre-owned and barely driven Subaru Outback.More information about the 2017 Subaru Outback:The genius of the Outback has always been its ability to straddle classifications, it helped create the crossover segment in the 1990s. As such, the Outback competes with family cars, SUVs and, of course, other crossover vehicles. With a base price just short of $25,000, the Outback should be affordable enough for families considering a new Camry or Accord. With better off-road credentials and a more usable luggage compartment, the Outback offers increased versatility over plain Jane family sedans. At the same time, the Subaru Outback offers the kind of fuel economy that most mid-sized SUVs struggle to match.Interesting features of this model are fuel-efficient transmissions, standard all-wheel drive, good ground clearance, Versatility, and spacious interior

Welcome to Exit5 Auto Group, where we've been helping the Capital Regions car lovers since 2016! We are a full-service dealership that specializes in pre-owned vehicles. Whether you need a quick fix, want to buy parts, or just want your car to look its best, we've got you covered.

If you're looking to purchase a reliable pre-owned vehicle, we can help there too. We can assist you with financing and even offer mechanical protection plans to reduce the overall cost of ownership. Every car we sell has been carefully inspected by one of our Master Certified technicians, who give it a thorough 125-point inspection. And don't worry, we also provide a free Carfax report to give you peace of mind.

We know that our customers are busy, so we've made it easy for you to shop for a car. description: The 2017 Subaru Outback 3.6R Limited AWD is a versatile and upscale wagon that combines strong performance, comfort, and all-weather capability. Powered by a robust 3.6L six-cylinder engine and Subarus symmetrical all-wheel-drive system, it delivers smooth acceleration and confident handling in a variety of road conditions. The Limited trim adds premium features including leather seating, heated front and rear seats, a power moonroof, advanced infotainment, and enhanced safety technology. Known for its spacious interior, generous cargo capacity, and elevated ride height, the Outback 3.6R Limited is an excellent choice for drivers seeking reliability, practicality, and refined capability in a crossover-style wagon. This is a one-owner personal vehicle last owned in Illinois, offering a straightforward and transparent ownership history. The last reported odometer reading of 111,621 miles is reasonable for a single-owner vehicle, and the 27 service history records reflect a strong pattern of regular and well-documented maintenance. description:
CARFAX One-Owner 2017 Subaru Outback 2.5i Limited AWD in Crystal White Pearl. This well-equipped Outback is built for Spokane and North Idaho driving, offering strong winter capability, premium comfort, and Subarus advanced safety systems. With Symmetrical All-Wheel Drive, heated front and rear seats, HID headlights, and windshield wiper de-icer, it is ideal for snowy commutes across Spokane Valley, Airway Heights, Cheney, and Coeur dAlene.
The Limited trim adds leather-trimmed upholstery, power driver and passenger seats, memory driver seat, dual-zone climate control, power moonroof, auto-dimming mirror, and a premium cabin designed for year-round comfort. The available Eyesight package includes Adaptive Cruise Control, Lane Departure Warning, Pre-Collision Braking, High Beam Assist, and Reverse Automatic Braking for added confidence on winter roads.
Technology features include the Subaru Starlink 7.0-inch Navigation System, harman/kardon Surround Sound with 12 speakers, smartphone integration, SiriusXM capability, Aha, Bluetooth, steering-wheel audio controls, Vehicle Information Display, and paddle-shift control switches. Convenience features include a power liftgate, heated mirrors, roof rack, rear seat back protector, splash guards, and all-weather floor mats.
Performance comes from the 2.5L BOXER engine paired with the Lineartronic CVT, delivering smooth handling and impressive efficiency at 25/32 MPG City/Highway. Four-wheel independent suspension, 4-wheel disc brakes, traction control, and stability control contribute to secure handling on icy and wet surfaces common around Spokane and Mt. Spokane.
Additional highlights include 18-inch alloy wheels, HID headlights, fog lights, heated rear seats, exterior auto-dimming mirrors with blind-spot detection, rear cross-traffic alert, rearview camera, emergency communication system, and multiple cargo-friendly features.
The 2017 Outback is an award winner, including IIHS Top Safety Pick+, ALG Residual Value Award, and multiple KBB honors for Best Family Cars, Best All-Wheel-Drive Vehicles Under $25,000, Most Comfortable Cars Under $30,000, and 5-Year Cost to Own.
This Outback 2.5i Limited offers capability, safety, and comfort ideal for the Inland Northwest. Perfect for winter travel, weekend mountain trips, or everyday commuting across the Spokane

description: The 2005 Toyota Camry LE presents a comfortable and reliable driving experience, well-suited for daily commuting or longer road trips. Known for its smooth ride and dependable performance, this midsize sedan features a refined 2.4-liter 4-cylinder engine paired with a smooth-shifting automatic transmission, delivering a solid balance of power and fuel efficiency. The Camry LE's spacious interior offers ample seating for five passengers, with cloth upholstery and supportive seats designed for all-day comfort. Its suspension is tuned for comfort, absorbing road imperfections with ease, and steering is light yet responsive, making city driving and highway cruising equally effortless.----This particular model comes well-equipped with automatic climate control, a premium feature for its class during its time, allowing both driver and passengers to maintain a consistent and comfortable interior temperature without the need for constant adjustment. Keyless entry adds convenience, enabling quick access to the vehicle without fumbling for keysideal for busy lifestyles or on-the-go errands. The dashboard layout is intuitive, with controls placed within easy reach and clear, legible gauges. Storage is generous, including a sizable trunk and multiple compartments in the cabin for personal items. Safety features include front airbags, anti-lock brakes, and seatbelt pretensioners. Overall, the 2005 Camry LE continues to uphold Toyota's reputation for long-lasting quality and practicality, making it a sensible choice for budget-conscious drivers seeking reliability and comfort in a well-rounded sedan.
